YaHei\', SimSun, \'Arial Narrow\'; line-height: 34px;\">碳水化合物：一片面包或一个蒸土豆</span><br style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: \'Microsoft YaHei\', SimSun, \'Arial Narrow\'; line-height: 34px;\" /><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: \'Microsoft YaHei\', SimSun, \'Arial Narrow\'; line-height: 34px;\">蛋白质：一个蛋清、蛋白奶</span><br style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: \'Microsoft YaHei\', SimSun, \'Arial Narrow\'; line-height: 34px;\" /><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: \'Microsoft YaHei\', SimSun, \'Arial Narrow\'; line-height: 34px;\">蔬菜水果：一个香蕉或猕猴桃</span>');
INSERT INTO `sx_article_data_21` VALUES ('55', '&nbsp;核心提示：都说春天是吃野菜的好时节，近年来兴起的健康食材自然少不了野菜的功劳。新鲜健康又美味的野菜是很多人的心头好，但是，大家都了解野菜吗？<br />\r\n<p><strong>苦菜</strong><strong>：清热燥湿</strong></p>\r\n<p>苦菜在我国大部分地区有生长，又叫苦蕈菜、苣菜、败酱等。苦菜顾名就能知其属性是味苦性寒，清热解毒，消肿排脓。苦菜中还含维生素C及大量铁元素，蛋白质、脂肪、糖类、胡萝卜素、维生素B及钙、磷等。此时食用可以清热凉血，降内热、减少因内热而外感风寒的疾病。</p>\r\n<p><strong>苋菜</strong><strong>：滋阴润燥</strong></p>\r\n<p>苋菜亦称为&ldquo;凫葵&rdquo;、&ldquo;荇菜&rdquo;、&ldquo;莕菜&rdquo;。其菜身软滑而菜味浓，入口甘香，有润肠胃清热毒的功效。苋菜能维持正常的心肌活动，防止肌肉痉挛。这是因为它含有丰富的铁，可合成红细胞中的血红蛋白，有携带氧气的功能。同时，它富含钙和维生素K，可以促进凝血、造血等功能。</p>\r\n<p><strong>马兰头</strong><strong>：清火明目</strong></p>\r\n<p>马兰头，又叫马兰、螃蜞头草、田边菊等，我国大部分地区路边及田野有生长，也有人工栽培。马兰头含丰富的维生素C、维生素A、蛋白质、脂肪、钙、铁等，味辛性凉清热解毒，对于口腔溃疡、咽喉肿痛、衄血、血痢等都有一定食疗作用。我们把马兰煮熟加调味后，美味可口，为家庭喜食的蔬菜之一，并有一定的药用价值，经常食用可达清火明目的目的。</p>\r\n<p><strong>荠菜：健脾和胃</strong></p>\r\n<p>荠菜，具有抗氧化的能力，在盛产的季节吃新鲜又有保健功效，可为一举两得的事情。荠菜又叫护生草、荠、芊菜、鸡心菜，目前除野生外，在我国各地均有栽培。在传统医书中皆有记载如《本草纲目》：&ldquo;明目益胃&rdquo;；《名医别录》：&ldquo;甘、温，无毒。和肝气，和中为上品&rdquo;；《日用本草》：&ldquo;凉肝明目&rdquo;。在春季养肝之时，食点荠菜正合时令。<br />\r\n<strong>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 刺儿菜：凉血祛淤</strong></p>\r\n<p>刺儿菜，它是菊科植物小蓟的全草或根，在我国大部分地区有生长，适应性很强，路旁、沟岸、田间可见，人们常称为小蓟、蓟蓟菜。刺儿菜含有蛋白质、脂肪、碳水化合物、膳食纤维、钙、磷、铁、胡萝卜素、维生素B、维生素B2、尼克酸和维生素C等成分。此外，还含有生物碱、胆碱、皂甙等。<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<strong>野菜好吃却不能任性，吃野菜的四项注意：</strong></p>\r\n<p><strong>1.&nbsp;不认识的不采、不吃。</strong>有的野菜看上去绿油油的很是可爱，但不一定能食用。采摘野菜时一定注意，不认识的不采、不吃。</p>\r\n<p><strong>2.&nbsp;路边的野菜不要采。</strong>路边生长的野菜容易受到污染，垃圾地上、路边的野菜不要采。</p>\r\n<p><strong>3.&nbsp;做好前处理。</strong>一些野菜有微毒，需要经过煮、浸泡才能去毒，一定要认真处理好后再吃。</p>\r\n<p><strong>4.&nbsp;野菜可不要贪吃。</strong>野菜毕竟是野菜，没有成为&ldquo;家常菜&rdquo;一定有它的原因，这是我们老祖宗在亲身实践中得来的经验，所以，尝尝鲜，偶尔改善改善口味还可以，不宜天天吃、吃很多。吃野菜原本是为了促进健康，如果吃的不合适带来负面作用，就适得其反啦。</p>');
INSERT INTO `sx_article_data_21` VALUES ('56', ' <span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 微软雅黑, 宋体; line-height: 26px;\">想要成为一名专业的厨娘，普通的家常菜是肯定是要会的。推荐8道好吃易做的家常菜做法，各位厨房新手老手都来学学。都是很受欢迎的家常菜哦。</span><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 微软雅黑, 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　糖醋排骨</p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 微软雅黑, 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　<img src=\"http://06.8660.org/file/upload/201604/09/0955564026.png\" style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 0px; color: transparent;\" alt=\"\" /></p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 微软雅黑, 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　糖醋排骨的做法</p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 微软雅黑, 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　主料：猪小排1000克</p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 微软雅黑, 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　调料：酱油15毫升、醋50毫升、葱1根、姜半块、八角2粒、花椒20粒、干辣椒2个、料酒15毫升、白糖20克</p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 微软雅黑, 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　糖醋排骨的做法：</p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 微软雅黑, 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　1.排骨、葱段、姜片放入锅中，加清水煮开后，撇去浮沫</p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 微软雅黑, 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　2.放入花椒大料干辣椒，煮至筷子能扎透，将排骨捞出</p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 微软雅黑, 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　3.煮排骨时，将醋、酱油、料酒、糖混合调匀成调料汁</p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 微软雅黑, 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　4.炒锅烧热，倒入调料汁</p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 微软雅黑, 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　5.待调料汁沸腾，倒入排骨，翻炒均匀</p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 微软雅黑, 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　6.倒入半碗煮排骨的汤，使汤汁完全没过排骨</p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 微软雅黑, 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　7.大火煮沸后调至小火炖煮</p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 微软雅黑, 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　8.待锅中汤汁收浓稠即可</p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 微软雅黑, 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　鱼香肉丝</p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 微软雅黑, 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　<img src=\"http://06.8660.org/file/upload/201604/09/0955564726.jpeg\" style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 0px; color: transparent;\" alt=\"\" /></p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 微软雅黑, 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　鱼香肉丝的做法：</p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 微软雅黑, 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　主料：猪里脊肉300克</p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 微软雅黑, 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　辅料：冬笋80克、黑木耳3朵、鸡蛋清1个</p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 微软雅黑, 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　调料：食盐3克、酱油15克、姜2片、蒜6瓣、料酒10克、米醋20克、淀粉15克、小葱2棵、泡红椒10克、白糖25克、植物油50克</p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 微软雅黑, 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　鱼香肉丝的做法：</p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 微软雅黑, 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　1.通脊片成片然后码放整齐准备切丝，如果有时候可以冻一下，然后再切丝会非常好切而且会非常工整</p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 微软雅黑, 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　2.切成丝然后泡在水里面，这样可以把肉丝里的血水泡出来，多换几次水，出来的肉丝会非常洁白漂亮</p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 微软雅黑, 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　3.泡白后放在笊篱里滗水，不用太干，因为肉丝需要有水，不然炒出来不会嫩了</p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 微软雅黑, 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　4.然后加少许盐和料酒腌下，再放蛋清抓匀，最后放干淀粉，然后放少许油封住，这样肉丝不会脱浆</p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 微软雅黑, 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　5.用好点的泡红椒，颜色和味道都会不同的</p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 微软雅黑, 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　6.所有调料的备齐</p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 微软雅黑, 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　7.泡红椒去籽剁碎，越烂越好，然后葱姜蒜切米备用，冬笋切和肉丝差不多的丝，木耳切丝，冬笋和木耳开水焯一下，沥干水备用</p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 微软雅黑, 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　8.重中之重，味汁(料酒10克、米醋20克、白糖25克、盐一点点、酱油15克、淀粉15克)，记住汁量不可大，不然炒出来汤汁太多，油稍多些，五成热时下泡椒和浆好的肉丝炒开，如果不好炒用筷子划拉，炒开立刻放葱姜蒜炒香，然后放入焯过的冬笋丝和木耳丝，最后倒入味汁，再炒几下就可以了<br /> </p>');
INSERT INTO `sx_article_data_21` VALUES ('57', '&nbsp;<span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 微软雅黑, 宋体; line-height: 26px;\">糖醋鲤鱼</span>\r\n<p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 微软雅黑, 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　<img src=\"http://06.8660.org/file/upload/201604/09/1000449926.jpeg\" style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 0px; color: transparent;\" alt=\"\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 微软雅黑, 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　糖醋鲤鱼的做法</p>\r\n<p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 微软雅黑, 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　主料：鲤鱼1条</p>\r\n<p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 微软雅黑, 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　辅料：鸡蛋1个、面粉2大勺</p>\r\n<p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 微软雅黑, 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　调料：花生油适量、食盐1勺、半蒜8瓣、生抽1小勺、米醋2大勺、淀粉1勺、水淀粉半碗、番茄酱2大勺、水1碗</p>\r\n<p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 微软雅黑, 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　糖醋鲤鱼的做法：</p>\r\n<p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 微软雅黑, 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　1.鲤鱼收拾干净后抽掉两面的腥筋，然后用刀倾斜45度角给鱼均匀的划斜开片</p>\r\n<p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 微软雅黑, 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　2.加盐1勺，在鱼身上下里外都用手将盐抹匀</p>\r\n<p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 微软雅黑, 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　3.盆里加入面粉2大勺，淀粉1勺，鸡蛋1个，清水1碗，调成糊后将鱼放入</p>\r\n<p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 微软雅黑, 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　4.提着鱼尾，将鱼通身挂上面糊</p>\r\n<p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 微软雅黑, 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　5.拿出后再在鱼身上两面都洒一层干面粉，并抖掉多余的部分</p>\r\n<p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 微软雅黑, 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　6.锅内放入足够多的油，七成热的时候，将鱼弯成弧形放入，小火炸。炸时可以用两只锅铲按住鲤鱼定型</p>\r\n<p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 微软雅黑, 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　7.将两面炸至微黄，鱼熟透，即可捞出</p>\r\n<p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 微软雅黑, 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　8.捞出的鱼稍晾凉一会，或者凉透也行</p>\r\n<p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 微软雅黑, 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　9.再回锅炸第二遍，一直要用小火，防止外皮焦糊</p>\r\n<p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 微软雅黑, 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　10.炸至鱼通体深黄即可捞入鱼盘中，尾巴向上的放</p>\r\n<p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 微软雅黑, 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　11.另起一锅，放少许油，小火，油温热时加入蒜碎炒香，千万别大火那样蒜碎会糊掉的</p>\r\n<p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 微软雅黑, 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　12.当闻到蒜香味时，加入半碗清水，番茄酱2大勺，米醋2大勺，生抽1小勺，煮开</p>\r\n<p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 微软雅黑, 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　13.倒入水淀粉小半碗，拌匀后加小半勺盐，再次煮开即可关火</p>\r\n<p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 微软雅黑, 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　14.趁热将酸甜汁浇在鱼上即可上桌</p>\r\n<p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 微软雅黑, 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　五花肉炒西兰花</p>\r\n<p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 微软雅黑, 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　<img src=\"http://06.8660.org/file/upload/201604/09/1000447726.jpeg\" style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 0px; color: transparent;\" alt=\"\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 微软雅黑, 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　五花肉炒西兰花的做法</p>\r\n<p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 微软雅黑, 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　主料：五花肉250g、西兰花500g</p>\r\n<p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 微软雅黑, 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　调料：食盐适量、鸡精适量、调和油适量</p>\r\n<p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 微软雅黑, 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　五花肉炒西兰花的做法：</p>\r\n<p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 微软雅黑, 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　1.选取肥中带瘦的五花肉。</p>\r\n<p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 微软雅黑, 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　2.切成薄薄的片儿。</p>\r\n<p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 微软雅黑, 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　3.放上点盐 酱油腌至着。</p>\r\n<p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 微软雅黑, 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　4.将西兰花弄成小块，然后洗净后放入锅里焯水。</p>\r\n<p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 微软雅黑, 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　5.开火倒油，把五花肉放进去翻炒。</p>\r\n<p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 微软雅黑, 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　6.等肉变色的时候，放上西兰花翻炒。大火。</p>\r\n<p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 微软雅黑, 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　7.放上一小勺的盐。翻炒。</p>\r\n<p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 微软雅黑, 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　8.放点鸡精。</p>\r\n<p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 微软雅黑, 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　继续大火翻炒。</p>\r\n<p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 微软雅黑, 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　9.OK，美味的下饭菜出锅了</p>\r\n<p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 微软雅黑, 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　家常小炒肉</p>\r\n<p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 微软雅黑, 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　<img src=\"http://06.8660.org/file/upload/201604/09/1000441526.jpeg\" style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 0px; color: transparent;\" alt=\"\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 微软雅黑, 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　家常小炒肉的做法</p>\r\n<p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 微软雅黑, 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　主料：猪肉(后臀尖)200克</p>\r\n<p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 微软雅黑, 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　辅料：红尖椒20克、尖椒30克、蒜苗20克</p>\r\n<p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 微软雅黑, 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　调料：食盐1小匙、酱油1小匙、鸡精少许、料酒2小匙、白糖1/2小匙、植物油1大匙</p>\r\n<p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 微软雅黑, 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　家常小炒肉的做法：</p>\r\n<p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 微软雅黑, 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　1、取带皮的乳猪五花肉，切成柳叶片</p>\r\n<p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 微软雅黑, 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　2、加湿淀粉、鸡蛋、精盐、酱油搅拌均匀</p>\r\n<p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 微软雅黑, 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　3、放入4成热油滑散捞出</p>\r\n<p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 微软雅黑, 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　4、锅内留油少许，放入姜丝、葱丝、滴醋烹出香味</p>\r\n<p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 微软雅黑, 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　5、下白糖、甜面酱、黄酱炒出酱香味</p>\r\n<p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 微软雅黑, 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　6、倒入肉片、木耳、黄花菜段、草菇片速炒出锅即成</p>\r\n<p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 微软雅黑, 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　7、食时，将生葱丝、面酱、肉片放入蒸熟的夹层饼里即可</p>\r\n<p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 微软雅黑, 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　麻婆豆腐</p>\r\n<p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 微软雅黑, 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　<img src=\"http://06.8660.org/file/upload/201604/09/1000447926.jpeg\" style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 0px; color: transparent;\" alt=\"\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 微软雅黑, 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　麻婆豆腐的做法</p>\r\n<p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 微软雅黑, 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　主料：南豆腐500克</p>\r\n<p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 微软雅黑, 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　辅料：牛肉100克</p>\r\n<p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 微软雅黑, 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　调料：食盐少许、酱油5克、姜5克、蒜5克、花椒5克、料酒5克、郫县豆瓣酱5克、辣椒粉3克、小葱5克、白糖3克、植物油适量</p>\r\n<p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 微软雅黑, 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　麻婆豆腐的做法：</p>\r\n<p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 微软雅黑, 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　1.葱姜蒜切小粒，郫县豆瓣酱剁碎备用</p>\r\n<p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 微软雅黑, 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　2.牛肉切成小粒备用</p>\r\n<p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 微软雅黑, 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　3.花椒干锅小火烘至棕红色取出，擀成细面备用</p>\r\n<p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 微软雅黑, 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　4.豆腐切小块，入加了盐的开水中焯至浮起，捞出沥干</p>\r\n<p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 微软雅黑, 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　5.起油锅，温油下牛肉粒煸炒至酥香吐油</p>\r\n<p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 微软雅黑, 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　6.下入郫县豆瓣酱和辣椒面中小火煸炒至香味和红油出</p>\r\n<p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 微软雅黑, 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　7.下入葱姜末继续小火煸炒</p>\r\n<p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 微软雅黑, 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　8.添加盐、糖、酱油和料酒，加一点热水烧开</p>\r\n<p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 微软雅黑, 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　9.添加豆腐，烧开后中火收汁</p>\r\n<p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 微软雅黑, 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　10.勾点薄芡，推匀，撒上蒜苗(葱花)和备好的花椒面即可</p>\r\n<p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 微软雅黑, 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">文章来源：1163029295@qq.com</p>');
INSERT INTO `sx_article_data_21` VALUES ('58', ' <span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 微软雅黑, 宋体; line-height: 26px;\">麻婆豆腐</span><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 微软雅黑, 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　<img src=\"http://06.8660.org/file/upload/201604/09/1004003426.jpeg\" style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 0px; color: transparent;\" alt=\"\" /></p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 微软雅黑, 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　麻婆豆腐的做法</p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 微软雅黑, 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　主料：南豆腐500克</p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 微软雅黑, 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　辅料：牛肉100克</p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 微软雅黑, 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　调料：食盐少许、酱油5克、姜5克、蒜5克、花椒5克、料酒5克、郫县豆瓣酱5克、辣椒粉3克、小葱5克、白糖3克、植物油适量</p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 微软雅黑, 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　麻婆豆腐的做法：</p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 微软雅黑, 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　1.葱姜蒜切小粒，郫县豆瓣酱剁碎备用</p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 微软雅黑, 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　2.牛肉切成小粒备用</p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 微软雅黑, 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　3.花椒干锅小火烘至棕红色取出，擀成细面备用</p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 微软雅黑, 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　4.豆腐切小块，入加了盐的开水中焯至浮起，捞出沥干</p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 微软雅黑, 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　5.起油锅，温油下牛肉粒煸炒至酥香吐油</p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 微软雅黑, 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　6.下入郫县豆瓣酱和辣椒面中小火煸炒至香味和红油出</p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 微软雅黑, 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　7.下入葱姜末继续小火煸炒</p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 微软雅黑, 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　8.添加盐、糖、酱油和料酒，加一点热水烧开</p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 微软雅黑, 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　9.添加豆腐，烧开后中火收汁</p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 微软雅黑, 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　10.勾点薄芡，推匀，撒上蒜苗(葱花)和备好的花椒面即可</p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 微软雅黑, 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　宫保鸡丁</p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 微软雅黑, 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　<img src=\"http://06.8660.org/file/upload/201604/09/1004009226.jpeg\" style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 0px; color: transparent;\" alt=\"\" /></p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 微软雅黑, 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　宫保鸡丁的做法</p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 微软雅黑, 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　主料：鸡腿4个</p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 微软雅黑, 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　辅料：花生10克、鸡蛋1个、葱30克、姜3片、蒜3瓣、干辣椒3个、花椒5粒、色拉油适量</p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 微软雅黑, 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　调料：食盐适量、酱油适量、醋1/2茶匙、料酒1茶匙、淀粉1茶匙、糖适量、辣椒(红，尖，干)(面)1/2茶</p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 微软雅黑, 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　宫保鸡丁的做法：</p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 微软雅黑, 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　1.鸡腿去骨去皮，洗净切成鸡丁。放入盐、淀粉、料酒、蛋清抓匀，腌制2小时以上，让鸡丁充分吸收调料</p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 微软雅黑, 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　2.花生米放入油锅中炸一下，捞出备用</p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 微软雅黑, 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　3.辣椒面和醋放在一起准备好</p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 微软雅黑, 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　4.姜切片、大葱只要中间的嫩芯，把葱芯切段</p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 微软雅黑, 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　5.将锅烧热，放入适量色拉油，放入葱姜蒜炒出香味</p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 微软雅黑, 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　6.放入干辣椒、花椒翻炒</p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 微软雅黑, 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　7.接着放入腌制好的鸡丁，翻炒变色</p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 微软雅黑, 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　8.放入酱油、辣椒面和醋、糖调味</p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 微软雅黑, 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　9.放入花生米翻炒均匀即可出锅</p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 微软雅黑, 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　香芋扣肉</p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 微软雅黑, 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　<img src=\"http://06.8660.org/file/upload/201604/09/1004005026.jpeg\" style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 0px; color: transparent;\" alt=\"\" /></p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 微软雅黑, 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　香芋扣肉的做法</p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 微软雅黑, 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　主料：五花肉适量</p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 微软雅黑, 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　辅料：葱适量、蒜适量、芋头适量</p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 微软雅黑, 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　调料：食盐少许、冰糖少许、八角适量、花椒少许、生抽适量、老抽适量、肉桂(叶)适量、白砂糖少许、胡椒粉少许、腐乳(红)少许、豆豉适量</p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 微软雅黑, 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　香芋扣肉的做法：</p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 微软雅黑, 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　第一步：</p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 微软雅黑, 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　1.将五花肉切成方形洗净备用;</p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 微软雅黑, 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　2.准备葱结、姜片、肉桂叶、八角、花椒、冰糖;</p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 微软雅黑, 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　3.选用一口较深的锅，注水高过肉面，将肉及2中材料放入，大火煮开，转中小火煮约半个钟;</p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 微软雅黑, 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　4.五花肉煮至可以用支筷子提起来，生熟度正好，起锅;</p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 微软雅黑, 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　5.用竹签在五花肉皮上扎小孔，以便入味及下油锅时爆油轻微些。</p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 微软雅黑, 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　6.乘热抹一层酱油(生抽+老抽，酱色以个人喜好调节.)</p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 微软雅黑, 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　第二步：</p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 微软雅黑, 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　1.将超市买回的香芋去皮清洗干净后，切成厚度均匀的大块;</p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 微软雅黑, 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　2.将每块香芋片薄薄地抹一层盐，腌制(10分钟左右)备用;</p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 微软雅黑, 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　3.起油锅，炸香芋片，强烈推荐油锅先炸香芋再炸五花肉，炸过肉的油会带色，再炸香芋就不够漂亮;</p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 微软雅黑, 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　4.香芋炸至两面表皮变硬，捞起控油备用;</p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 微软雅黑, 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　5.五花肉下油锅前抹一层白醋，(老妈秘笈，抹醋再炸肉皮够酥)</p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 微软雅黑, 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　6.五花肉开炸，呵呵，很热闹的哦，注意加盖，以免误伤;</p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 微软雅黑, 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　第三步：</p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 微软雅黑, 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　1.五花肉炸至金黄起锅，控油后放入刚开始煮肉的水中浸泡;</p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 微软雅黑, 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　2.泡至肉肉皮如图中所示蓬松起皱的状态即可，(如果赶时间，可以将锅放灶上稍煮一会)</p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 微软雅黑, 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　3.调酱汁：将制作调料加上蒜泥，混合调匀备用;</p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 微软雅黑, 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　4.将泡好水的五花肉，切片，加入3中调好的酱汁，拌匀，稍加腌制(约15分钟)备用;</p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 微软雅黑, 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　5.将五花肉和炸好的香芋片相间排列在一只大碗里，上蒸锅蒸;</p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 微软雅黑, 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　6.大火蒸约1个钟(时间长点更好)，起锅倒扣，将蒸肉的汤汁加热收浓浇上，即可摆盘上桌。<br />文章来源：1163029295@qq.com</p>');
INSERT INTO `sx_article_data_21` VALUES ('59', ' <span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px;\">生活不止眼前的苟且，还有诗和远方的田野。</span><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　你赤手空拳来到人世间为找到那片海不顾一切......</p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　许巍《生活不止眼前的苟且》</p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------</p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　有人爱吃肉，无肉不欢，无肉不成席。</p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　有人爱吃素，清心寡欲，修养身心。</p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　我说荤素搭配，既营养又美味，何乐不为？</p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　再次来到南城探寻美味，总觉得这边回民居多，羊肉也比较正宗。</p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　<img src=\"http://06.8660.org/file/upload/201604/09/1011056226.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 0px; color: transparent; max-width: 600px;\" /></p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　[羊煮艺羊蝎子火锅 ]</p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　地址：红星街13号（离宋家庄地铁站两三站公交）</p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　人均：70-80元</p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　<img src=\"http://06.8660.org/file/upload/201604/09/1011052726.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 0px; color: transparent; max-width: 600px;\" /></p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　必点1</p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　[精品传统大锅 ]</p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　特点：汤汁用二十余种中草药熬制；肉质软烂不塞牙。</p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　羊蝎子火锅按大小份，满满的一锅，那种带一点筋下边还藏着脆骨的羊蝎子最后吃。<span style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">师傅手艺不错，不愧是开了十余年的老店。</span></p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　<img src=\"http://06.8660.org/file/upload/201604/09/1011054826.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 0px; color: transparent; max-width: 600px;\" /></p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　↑↑羊蝎子吃完不过瘾，又来了一大份肉多的羊脖，同样很美味。</p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　<img src=\"http://06.8660.org/file/upload/201604/09/1011051826.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 0px; color: transparent; max-width: 600px;\" /></p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　↑↑↑主打菜吃完可以接着涮羊肉。一锅两吃。</p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　[自卷羔羊肉 ] 32元一大盘，非常鲜美，特别整齐干净，肉质不散也不冒血水。</p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　<img src=\"http://06.8660.org/file/upload/201604/09/1011055726.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 0px; color: transparent; max-width: 600px;\" /></p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　[麻将小料 ] 芝麻味十足，特别浓稠</p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　<img src=\"http://06.8660.org/file/upload/201604/09/1011053426.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 0px; color: transparent; max-width: 600px;\" /></p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　[菌类拼牌 ] 延年益寿，抗氧化，大家都知道的养生菜品。</p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　<img src=\"http://06.8660.org/file/upload/201604/09/1011054826.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 0px; color: transparent; max-width: 600px;\" /></p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　[全家福 ] 蔬菜满满的，实惠。</p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　↓↓↓必点2</p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　锦州风味烧烤也是他家特色</p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　<img src=\"http://06.8660.org/file/upload/201604/09/1011057526.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 0px; color: transparent; max-width: 600px;\" /></p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　[羊肉串 ] 两元一串，两元现在能买神马？值！！！</p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　<img src=\"http://06.8660.org/file/upload/201604/09/1011058726.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 0px; color: transparent; max-width: 600px;\" /></p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　【鸡爪】10元一份，三大串，肉质很厚实。</p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　<img src=\"http://06.8660.org/file/upload/201604/09/1011056226.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 0px; color: transparent; max-width: 600px;\" /></p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　[盐烤大虾 ]</p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　<img src=\"http://06.8660.org/file/upload/201604/09/1011051426.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 0px; color: transparent; max-width: 600px;\" /></p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　[烤蚕蛹和烤鸡头 ]</p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　<img src=\"http://06.8660.org/file/upload/201604/09/1011059926.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 0px; color: transparent; max-width: 600px;\" /></p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　↑↑↑虾和蚕蛹都很丰满，口感很独特。</p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　<img src=\"http://06.8660.org/file/upload/201604/09/1011059326.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 0px; color: transparent; max-width: 600px;\" /></p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　[烤羊排 ] 一定要尝尝！外皮微微焦炭化，三分肥七分瘦，真的很好吃！！！</p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　↓↓↓必点3</p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　<img src=\"http://06.8660.org/file/upload/201604/09/1011059126.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 0px; color: transparent; max-width: 600px;\" /></p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　[炸窝头配臭豆腐 ]</p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　喜欢臭豆腐的人觉得它越吃越香，拿一块窝头，在上边像抹黄油一样在抹上一层腐乳，间或来上几根老北京的咸菜疙瘩，吃的就是这么魔性！！！<br />文章来源：一只特立独行的喵~~~1163029295@qq.com</p>');
INSERT INTO `sx_article_data_21` VALUES ('60', ' <p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\"><img src=\"http://06.8660.org/file/upload/201604/09/1018088926.jpg\" style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 0px; color: transparent; max-width: 650px;\" alt=\"\" /></p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　图文：凯德印象</p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　春天豌豆上市的季节，童年的记忆里全都是豌豆饭，奶奶会亲手剥出最新鲜的豌豆，和糯米和咸肉一起在灶头大铁锅里翻炒，然后灶头里柴火烧起来。我们一帮小馋鬼围绕着灶头跑来跑去，听到铁锅里噼噼啪啪的声音出来，香味也跟着四散开来，于是都垫着脚尖开始迫不及待。奶奶会熄了灶火跑来喝止我们，把抹布铺在在大铁锅的木盖上。等一等，焖一焖，味道更好，香味更足。</p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　如今大城市的生活，早已没有慢下来的心情享受美味，做什么事情都是心急火燎的。周末在家一碗春天的碗豆饭，让自己慢下来。</p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　<img src=\"http://06.8660.org/file/upload/201604/09/1018086826.jpg\" style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 0px; color: transparent; max-width: 650px;\" alt=\"\" /></p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　【材料】豌豆、咸肉、鸡蛋、糯米或剩饭</p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　【简易DIY做法】</p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　1.新鲜的豌豆洗净，咸肉切片，鸡蛋炒散备用，可以用新鲜糯米，也可以用隔夜的剩饭。</p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　2.油锅烧热，依次加入咸肉和豌豆，轻轻翻炒至出香气。将炒散的鸡蛋放入，继续翻炒。</p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　3.如果是生米，则将炒好的材料和生米一起放进电饭煲煮熟即可。如果是隔夜的剩饭，则将剩饭倒入后继续翻炒，加两小勺水后关小火焖10分钟。</p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　4.最后盛饭前加入自己喜欢的豆瓣酱等调味即可。</p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　<img src=\"http://06.8660.org/file/upload/201604/09/1018086826.jpg\" style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 0px; color: transparent; max-width: 650px;\" alt=\"\" /></p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　<img src=\"http://06.8660.org/file/upload/201604/09/1018083626.jpg\" style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 0px; color: transparent; max-width: 650px;\" alt=\"\" /></p>文章来源：一只特立独行的喵Syca~~~~1163029295@qq.com');
INSERT INTO `sx_article_data_21` VALUES ('61', ' <p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\"><img src=\"http://06.8660.org/file/upload/201604/09/1023106826.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 0px; color: transparent; max-width: 600px;\" /></p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　“写文要找到‘泪点’，做菜要捉住‘痛点’”，如果一篇文章没有了让你有感触的节点，那这篇文章就没有了味道，同样做菜如果没捉住你的味蕾，那也不是咱喜欢的滋味。</p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　辣，是一种痛，是一种充满刺激的痛快淋漓的痛。明知是痛，我们又是那么的锲而不舍。</p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; word-wrap: break-word; text-indent: 0px;\"><font color=\"#333333\" face=\"宋体\"><span style=\"line-height: 26px;\">　　既然要找到用雪菜做菜的痛点，那么雪菜搭配着红椒与五花肉丁，完全可以制造一个小小的痛。肉末雪菜，这不是很“痛”的小菜，可雪菜特有的清香味道，加上鲜辣的红椒，也就成了一个可以拥有的“痛”。</span></font><br /><font color=\"#333333\" face=\"宋体\"><span style=\"line-height: 26px;\">文章来源：一只特立独行的喵Syca~~~~1163029295@qq.com</span></font></p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　<img src=\"http://06.8660.org/file/upload/201604/09/1023104726.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 0px; color: transparent; max-width: 600px;\" /></p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　<img src=\"http://06.8660.org/file/upload/201604/09/1023106326.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 0px; color: transparent; max-width: 600px;\" /></p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　<img src=\"http://06.8660.org/file/upload/201604/09/1023105726.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 0px; color: transparent; max-width: 600px;\" /></p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　1、干黄豆用清水洗净后倒入足量的清水浸泡一晚，泡至黄豆粒膨大后淘洗干净捞出备用。</p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　2、腌渍好的雪菜淘洗干净去掉脏污，切成指头肚大小的菜粒。</p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　3、生姜刮掉皮切成细粒，红尖椒择洗干净后切成辣椒碎。</p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　4、五花肉入稍微冷冻至能切动时取出，切成指头肚大小的肉粒。</p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　<img src=\"http://06.8660.org/file/upload/201604/09/1023102826.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 0px; color: transparent; max-width: 600px;\" /></p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　5、炒锅里倒入油，油热后倒入五花肉丁放入两个八角，小火把五花肉煸炒出油、肉粒松散。</p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　6、倒入红尖椒碎，小火翻炒出香辣味。</p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　7、倒入泡好的黄豆、添入足量的清水，开大火烧开后改小火煨炖40分钟。喜欢雪菜绵软口感的，可在这时放入雪菜与黄豆一起煨炖。</p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　8、炖至汤汁浓稠时，放入切好的雪菜粒，根据汤汁的咸淡调入适量的精盐，大火翻炒收汁。</p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　<img src=\"http://06.8660.org/file/upload/201604/09/1023102426.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 0px; color: transparent; max-width: 600px;\" /></p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　<img src=\"http://06.8660.org/file/upload/201604/09/1023106926.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 0px; color: transparent; max-width: 600px;\" /></p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　雪菜也叫雪里蕻或雪里红，雪菜为冬季时令蔬菜，可谓是家庭厨房里的常备装备。蕻的解释是茂盛的意思，雪里蕻就是冬季雪深，诸菜冻损，此菜独青的意思。南方叫雪菜，北方一般叫做雪里蕻，可能是与南方冬季没有北方雪多雪深有关吧。</p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; word-wrap: break-word; text-indent: 0px;\"><font color=\"#333333\" face=\"宋体\"><span style=\"line-height: 26px;\">　　</span></font><font face=\"宋体\"><span style=\"line-height: 26px; border-style: initial; border-color: initial; border-image-source: initial; border-image-slice: initial; border-image-width: initial; border-image-outset: initial; border-image-repeat: initial;\"><img src=\"http://06.8660.org/file/upload/201604/09/1023108926.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 0px; color: transparent; max-width: 600px;\" /></span></font><br /><font color=\"#333333\" face=\"宋体\"><span style=\"line-height: 26px;\">~~~~一只特立独行的喵Syca~~~~1163029295@qq.com</span></font></p>');
INSERT INTO `sx_article_data_21` VALUES ('62', ' <strong style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-align: center; border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">玛德琳蛋糕</strong><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px; text-align: center;\">(法国贝壳形状的代表烘焙甜点）</p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　玛德琳蛋糕名字的由来有很多版本， 比较知名的是在前波兰国王斯坦尼斯拉斯公爵（路易十五的岳父）的宫廷中，由女仆玛德琳开始进行制作的。这款甜点深受国王的喜爱，因此取了这个名字。据说后来因为配方让嫁给了路易十五、住在凡尔赛宫的国王爱女玛丽蕾捷斯卡王妃带走了，进而传播到了法国。</p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　<img src=\"http://img.mp.itc.cn/upload/20160330/997dede8d9004def9d840631338e49c8_th.jpg\" style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 0px; color: transparent; max-width: 650px;\" alt=\"\" /></p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px; text-align: center;\"><strong style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">海绵蛋糕</strong></p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px; text-align: center;\">(大家都很喜欢的甜点之王)</p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　海绵蛋糕，就像它的名字一样，其意思是烘焙成如海绵般松软的甜点。这个名字来自美国，在法国叫做软饼，在15~16世纪产生，到了17世纪后，以法国的王室为中心，作为庆祝宴席的甜点而进行制作。据说从这个时候开始，关于甜点制作的专业书籍也大量出版，传播到了全法国。</p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　<img src=\"http://img.mp.itc.cn/upload/20160330/b87b1c0e123b49fe93baa091f6a3a529_th.jpg\" style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 0px; color: transparent; max-width: 650px;\" alt=\"\" /></p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px; text-align: center;\"><strong style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">磅蛋糕</strong></p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px; text-align: center;\">(重黄油蛋糕的代表)</p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　这是一款起源于英国的十分受欢迎的黄油蛋糕。由于制作材料黄油、鸡蛋、砂糖、低筋面粉各使用1磅（约450g）的量，因此被命名为“磅蛋糕”。在法国叫做“四个四分之一（quatre-quarts）”，意思是“4/4（4分之4）”，其也是源于使用同等分量的四种材料的缘故。</p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　<img src=\"http://img.mp.itc.cn/upload/20160330/58f530b2aafa4b00854fa373c8003f09_th.jpg\" style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 0px; color: transparent; max-width: 650px;\" alt=\"\" /></p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px; text-align: center;\"><strong style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">塔坦苹果挞</strong></p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px; text-align: center;\">(失败之作变得大受欢迎的苹果派)</p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　用米黄色的苹果制作成的香味醇厚的塔坦苹果挞，是在法国经营小旅馆的塔坦姐妹的失败尝试中产生的。本来应该在挞皮上面放上苹果和砂糖后进行烘烤的，但是塔坦姐妹忘记在模具中铺放挞皮了，然后中途尝试着将挞皮覆盖在苹果上面，焦糖熏染在了苹果上，便变成了十分好吃的挞了。以“塔坦姐妹烘烤的挞”的这个意思，取了这个名字。</p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　<img src=\"http://06.8660.org/file/upload/201604/09/1026373626.jpg\" style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 0px; color: transparent; max-width: 650px;\" alt=\"\" /></p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px; text-align: center;\"><strong style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">戚风蛋糕</strong></p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px; text-align: center;\">(道破了蛋糕松软的秘密)</p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　戚风在法语中的意思是“丝绸”。戚风蛋糕的历史始于1927年的美国，发明者是向洛杉矶的西餐厅批发面包的哈利·贝克（Harry Baker）。他一直将这款蛋糕的制作食谱秘密保存着，直至1947年卖给了通用磨坊食品公司（General Mills）后被公诸于世。从此大家明白了蛋糕松软的秘密便是打发的蛋白和植物油，一时在全美国成为热门话题。</p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　<img src=\"http://img.mp.itc.cn/upload/20160330/dd5bf05f5e2b4c18ad99733f45bd0ec0_th.jpg\" style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 0px; color: transparent; max-width: 650px;\" alt=\"\" /></p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; word-wrap: break-word; text-indent: 0px; text-align: center;\"><font color=\"#333333\" face=\"宋体\"><span style=\"line-height: 26px;\">图片来源于网络<br /></span></font><font color=\"#333333\" face=\"宋体\"><span style=\"line-height: 26px;\">~~~~一只特立独行的喵Syca~~~~1163029295@qq.com</span></font></p>');
INSERT INTO `sx_article_data_21` VALUES ('63', '&nbsp;<span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px;\">　　</span><img src=\"http://06.8660.org/file/upload/201604/09/1035185426.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 0px; color: transparent; max-width: 600px;\" />\r\n<p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　<span style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">喜欢这段话，对于生活的定义。miniko一直都觉得不管再累再忙，都不要丢了生活，丢了自己，所以</span><span style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">，每年固定会抽时间出国旅游，固定周末去附近的小镇或者山里玩一玩，给自己一点新鲜的空气，给自己一</span><span style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">点空余的时间，给自己一点点无人打扰的空间，做自己，调整心情。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　<span style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">上个月，miniko去了一次安仁古镇，多年前曾经去过，但是当时还未完全打造出来，这次去对安仁大为</span><span style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">改观，这个穿越到民国的古镇是如此的安静和典雅，与千篇一律的古镇截然不同。所以打算写个简单的攻略</span><span style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">分享给大家，分行程，美食，住宿和交通给大家分别介绍哦~反正miniko当时去的时候觉得这个地方不是那</span><span style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">么的拥挤，不像黄龙溪，洛带，街子那样的接踵摩肩，弥漫着人肉的味道，哈哈，反而比较有文化底蕴和小</span><span style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">资情怀。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　<img src=\"http://06.8660.org/file/upload/201604/09/1035187226.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 0px; color: transparent; max-width: 600px;\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　<span style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">&ldquo;川蜀之西，距成都一小时车程，这个曾惊艳了《中国国家地理》的小镇，在仅3.2平方公里的土地上，完</span><span style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">整保存着27座公馆与30万平米古宅建筑群，它是中国唯一的博物馆小镇，恢弘外表之下，有着一个婉约优</span><span style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">雅的名字&mdash;&mdash;安仁。&rdquo;（摘录于网络）</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　<img src=\"http://06.8660.org/file/upload/201604/09/1035185726.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 0px; color: transparent; max-width: 600px;\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　<span style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><strong style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(255, 104, 39);\">行程</span></strong></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　<span style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">周末2日游，第一天刘氏庄园+建川博物馆，晚上住安仁古街，第二天逛下白天的安仁古镇，回成都，交</span><span style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">通和住宿稍后有提到。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　<img src=\"http://06.8660.org/file/upload/201604/09/1035188026.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 0px; color: transparent; max-width: 600px;\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　<img src=\"http://06.8660.org/file/upload/201604/09/1035186526.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 0px; color: transparent; max-width: 600px;\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　<span style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">安仁古镇街道是miniko认为四川所有古镇最美的，头顶装饰的彩色油纸伞，很有越南岘港小镇的风情，遮</span><span style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">挡了现代，凝固了历史，顺带可以遮风挡雨，简直设计的不要太周到了，最关键的是拍照那是超美的~如果</span><span style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">能再摇曳一身旗袍就圆满了，只是这身材穿个旗袍估计很吃力~那就换个学生服吧，也是不错的~</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　<img src=\"http://06.8660.org/file/upload/201604/09/1035188026.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 0px; color: transparent; max-width: 600px;\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　<span style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">古街上公馆林立，多有&ldquo;庭院深深深几许&rdquo;之意，值得大家深入其中，定有惊喜。不止是庭院，就连两旁的</span><span style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">小店都超级精致小资的，包罗花店，客栈，咖啡店，杂货铺以及服装店等，其中穿插着民国风情的墙画，老</span><span style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">茶馆，历史博物馆~就连孔裔公学也在古街上~</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　<img src=\"http://06.8660.org/file/upload/201604/09/1035184026.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 0px; color: transparent; max-width: 600px;\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　<img src=\"http://06.8660.org/file/upload/201604/09/1035183126.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 0px; color: transparent; max-width: 600px;\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　<img src=\"http://06.8660.org/file/upload/201604/09/1035186226.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 0px; color: transparent; max-width: 600px;\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　<img src=\"http://06.8660.org/file/upload/201604/09/1035181826.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 0px; color: transparent; max-width: 600px;\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　<strong style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(255, 104, 39);\">美食</span></strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　<span style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">其实整条街都还不错哦~可能还没有太商业化，所以价格都还不算高，个人觉得这家&quot;杨醪糟&quot;真的很好吃！</span><span style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">基本上所有的菜品都很好吃，古镇特有的风味，推荐醪糟，各种口味都很好吃，现点现煮的，相当巴适，还</span><span style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">有狼牙土豆，基本每次都是2份2份的点，油炸豆腐抹的海椒香料也是绝了，性价比只高，点了一桌子，人均</span><span style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">才20元！！！杨醪糟请你考虑搬迁到miniko家楼下，天天我都来光顾好么？</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　<img src=\"http://06.8660.org/file/upload/201604/09/1035187926.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 0px; color: transparent; max-width: 600px;\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　<img src=\"http://06.8660.org/file/upload/201604/09/1035181326.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 0px; color: transparent; max-width: 600px;\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　<img src=\"http://06.8660.org/file/upload/201604/09/1035187026.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 0px; color: transparent; max-width: 600px;\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　<img src=\"http://06.8660.org/file/upload/201604/09/1035185726.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 0px; color: transparent; max-width: 600px;\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　<img src=\"http://06.8660.org/file/upload/201604/09/1035182126.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 0px; color: transparent; max-width: 600px;\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　<span style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">另外一家网上很多人推荐的就是游血旺啦~肥肠血旺miniko是非常爱的，酸辣可口，血旺嫩如婴儿肌肤一般</span><span style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">的鲜嫩，肥肠应该是miniko最喜欢的内脏第一名，第二是千层肚，哈哈，口味就是介么重！除了肥肠血旺</span><span style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">还有石磨豆花、地主排骨、藿香鲫鱼、焦皮肘子、豆腐土鲢鱼、土九碗等也是好吃得很~</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　<img src=\"http://06.8660.org/file/upload/201604/09/1035185226.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 0px; color: transparent; max-width: 600px;\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　<img src=\"http://06.8660.org/file/upload/201604/09/1035189926.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 0px; color: transparent; max-width: 600px;\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　<img src=\"http://06.8660.org/file/upload/201604/09/1035185426.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 0px; color: transparent; max-width: 600px;\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　<span style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">然后还有一家在电影院的对面，听说是一家开了很久的老馆子了，口碑也很好哈</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　<span style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">如果想要体验客栈的，可以当天去古镇走一圈再决定住哪里，价格从200-400不等~客栈的风格都挺不错的</span><span style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">，晚上睡觉很安静，完全不会觉得受打扰，感受一晚静谧的古镇时光吧~</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; word-wrap: break-word; text-indent: 0px;\"><font color=\"#333333\" face=\"宋体\"><span style=\"line-height: 26px;\">文章来源于网络</span></font></p>\r\n<p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; word-wrap: break-word; text-indent: 0px;\"><font color=\"#333333\" face=\"宋体\"><span style=\"line-height: 26px;\">~~~~一只特立独行的喵Syca~~~~1163029295@qq.com</span></font></p>');
INSERT INTO `sx_article_data_21` VALUES ('64', ' <span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px;\">许是生活在北方的缘故吧，我们家三天两头的吃面食。包子馒头面条，每天换着吃。最爱还是包子，我总是一次性蒸两斤，蒸熟晾凉了，冻冰箱。每天早晨再热一热，就可以当早点了。</span><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　包子这个东西，其实挺随意的。觉得什么好吃，就包什么口味的，把自己喜欢吃的菜混搭着包进去，或是把自己平时不大喜欢吃的混合喜欢的东西一起包进去。无论怎么做，都挺好吃。</p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　今天试着把粉条，混着五花肉，还有冬笋一起做成馅儿。冬笋是好食材，加进去，味道特别好。依然做炒馅儿的包子。味道挺好的。做的水煎包，香喷喷的。</p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　相对来说，我比较喜欢炒馅儿的包子，生肉馅儿的，总感觉有腥味。但还是看个人喜好了，有可能是我味觉比较敏感吧。别人都不觉得腥。</p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　<span style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">有时候蒸熟的包子，开锅一看一个个趴着，扁扁的，其实，只需要在包好包子后给它一个个往上提拉一下，蒸熟后就不会趴了，一个个特别立体。小窍门。跟着面点师学的。当然，面团也不能和的太软了。</span></p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　<img src=\"http://img.mp.itc.cn/upload/20160406/3e07ab5b1ce74ae8886b985a7e24d45d_th.jpg\" style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 0px; color: transparent; max-width: 650px;\" alt=\"\" /></p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　<img src=\"http://06.8660.org/file/upload/201604/11/1501171829.jpg\" style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 0px; color: transparent; max-width: 650px;\" alt=\"\" /></p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　包子皮材料</p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　面粉500克，水240克，酵母3克，糖40克</p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　包子馅儿材料</p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　五花肉300克，粉条120克，冬笋2个，</p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　辅料</p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　胡萝卜1个，香菇一把，葱姜各十克，蒜苗3棵。盐适量，十三香1茶匙，酱油2调羹。香油适量，盐适量</p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　1.五花肉切小丁，别太碎。粉条开水煮5分钟，捞出过凉水，切小段。香菇提前泡发剁碎，冬笋去皮擦丝，胡萝卜擦丝，葱姜，蒜苗，切碎。</p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　<img src=\"http://06.8660.org/file/upload/201604/11/1501174329.jpg\" style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 0px; color: transparent; max-width: 650px;\" alt=\"\" /></p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　<span style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">2.提前和面，500克 面粉加240克水，3克酵母，40克糖，和成光滑面团，发酵两倍大。发酵面团的同时，炒包子馅儿。多点油，爆香葱姜，香菇末。</span></p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　<img src=\"http://06.8660.org/file/upload/201604/11/1501176129.jpg\" style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 0px; color: transparent; max-width: 650px;\" alt=\"\" /></p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　<span style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">3.放入肉丁炒变色，加入十三香，酱油，加冬笋，翻炒。加一碗开水，煮一会儿，收汁加入胡萝卜丝</span></p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　<img src=\"http://06.8660.org/file/upload/201604/11/1501172829.jpg\" style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 0px; color: transparent; max-width: 650px;\" alt=\"\" /></p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　<span style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">4.最后关火，加入粉条，蒜苗，加适量盐，糖，调味。比平时炒菜略咸就可以了</span></p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　<img src=\"http://06.8660.org/file/upload/201604/11/1501176329.jpg\" style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 0px; color: transparent; max-width: 650px;\" alt=\"\" /></p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　<span style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">5.发酵好的面团，取出来排气</span></p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　<img src=\"http://06.8660.org/file/upload/201604/11/1501177929.jpg\" style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 0px; color: transparent; max-width: 650px;\" alt=\"\" /></p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　<span style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">6.分成一个个小剂子，大小看个人需要，我今天做的水煎包，做的比较小，所以分成25克每个的小剂子。比小笼包稍微大点。</span></p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　<img src=\"http://06.8660.org/file/upload/201604/11/1501175729.jpg\" style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 0px; color: transparent; max-width: 650px;\" alt=\"\" /></p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　<span style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">7.每个剂子搓圆擀成中间厚旁边薄的面皮。按自己喜欢的花样包起来。最重要的一点来了。包好的包子，每个收口的地方，用手提拉一下。让包子往下垂。包子站直了。一会儿蒸熟后就不会趴锅了</span></p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　<img src=\"http://06.8660.org/file/upload/201604/11/1501179129.jpg\" style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 0px; color: transparent; max-width: 650px;\" alt=\"\" /></p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　<span style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">8.包好后，盖上湿布，继续醒发，大约20分钟左右，看包子膨大点了，轻轻拍着有弹性时，就可以或蒸，或煎了。我今天做了水煎包。平底锅放油， 有猪油最好。更香。小火，摆上包子</span></p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　<img src=\"http://06.8660.org/file/upload/201604/11/1501177029.jpg\" style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 0px; color: transparent; max-width: 650px;\" alt=\"\" /></p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　<span style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">9.待包子底部结一层硬皮有点变色时，倒入没过包子一半的热水。盖锅盖，大火烧开，再中火。。</span></p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　<img src=\"http://06.8660.org/file/upload/201604/11/1501177429.jpg\" style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 0px; color: transparent; max-width: 650px;\" alt=\"\" /></p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　<span style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">10.水都烧干了时，再加点油，大火顶一下。包子底会脆脆的。很好吃。</span></p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　<img src=\"http://06.8660.org/file/upload/201604/11/1501175929.jpg\" style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 0px; color: transparent; max-width: 650px;\" alt=\"\" /></p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　小贴士</p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　包子的大小，看自己喜好。包子馅，如果不喜欢熟的，可以用生肉馅。粉条的馅儿真好吃。加了冬笋整体味道很好。蒜苗提味效果特别好。</p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; word-wrap: break-word; text-indent: 0px;\"><font color=\"#333333\" face=\"宋体\"><span style=\"line-height: 26px;\">文章来源于网络</span></font></p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; word-wrap: break-word; text-indent: 0px;\"><font color=\"#333333\" face=\"宋体\"><span style=\"line-height: 26px;\">一只特立独行的喵Syca~~~~1163029295@qq.com</span></font></p>');
INSERT INTO `sx_article_data_21` VALUES ('65', '<p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　<img src=\"http://06.8660.org/file/upload/201604/11/1505314529.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 0px; color: transparent; max-width: 600px;\" /></p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　新买了烤箱，但还没有都不会做？</p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　肿么办？</p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　教你一个新技能，</p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　“香蕉一口酥”。</p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　外酥里软，满嘴浓郁的香蕉味！</p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　既能满足口欲，而且也很有格调呢。</p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　<strong style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">【香蕉一口酥】</strong></p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　食材：</p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　香蕉1根、千层饼皮1张</p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　做法：</p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　1. 备好所需食材；</p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　2. 香蕉去皮，置于千层饼皮上；</p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　3. 从一边将饼皮卷起，并且将香蕉卷紧；</p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　4. 卷好后，用到切成均等小份儿；</p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　5. 整齐码放在烤盘上，烤箱预热，温度200度，时间5分钟即可。</p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　<img src=\"http://06.8660.org/file/upload/201604/11/1505317729.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 0px; color: transparent; max-width: 600px;\" /></p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　碎碎念：</p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　千层饼皮在超市或淘宝都很容易买到，自己做也可以，但是很麻烦，买现成的快捷方便。</p>');
INSERT INTO `sx_article_data_21` VALUES ('66', '&nbsp;<span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px;\">肝脏是人体内脏中最大的器官，发挥着重要的&ldquo;新陈代谢&rdquo;功能，是人体的解毒器官。肝脏不断对流过的血液进行解毒，以维持人体的正常运动。肝脏一旦受损，肝脏解毒功能下降，血液中的毒素会迅速增加，导致其他器官也加速衰老。由此可见肝脏对于人体健康发挥着至关重要的作用。 那么在生活中，如果肝脏出现了问题会有什么表现呢？快来看看究竟哪些是肝脏发出的&ldquo;求救&rdquo;信号，让我们对肝脏受损早知道。</span>\r\n<p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　1.喝酒易醉</p>\r\n<p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　<img src=\"http://06.8660.org/file/upload/201604/11/1510487029.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 0px; color: transparent; max-width: 600px;\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　有些人以前酒量很大，不会轻易喝醉，但是在最近一段时间，好像很容易喝醉，酒量大不如前。有些人会感叹自己&ldquo;老了&rdquo;，其实不然，这可能就是肝脏在求救了。肝功能下降，无法完全分解酒精代谢物乙醛，才会让&ldquo;千杯不倒&rdquo;变成&ldquo;一滴飘&rdquo;。</p>\r\n<p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　2.粉刺增多</p>\r\n<p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　<img src=\"http://06.8660.org/file/upload/201604/11/1510488829.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 0px; color: transparent; max-width: 600px;\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　有些人原来脸上干干净净，但最近不断冒痘痘，而且层出不穷。现在的当务之急并不是用什么化妆品可以祛痘，而应该关注一下肝脏健康了。人体中的黄体荷尔蒙有促进分泌皮脂的作用，肝脏可以调节该荷尔蒙含量，以达到身体可适应的最佳状态，肝脏功能下降会导致皮脂分泌增多，粉刺增多。</p>\r\n<p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　3.伤口易化脓感染</p>\r\n<p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　<img src=\"http://06.8660.org/file/upload/201604/11/1510486729.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 0px; color: transparent; max-width: 600px;\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　如果伤口流血不止，不容易愈合，甚至出现化脓感染的情况，那么就要提高警惕了。如果肝脏功能受损会造成凝血因子合成障碍和皮肤再生障碍，导致伤口流血不止或不易愈合。另外，肝脏解毒功能下降，易造成伤口感染细菌，导致化脓。</p>\r\n<p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　4.鼻头发红</p>\r\n<p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　<img src=\"http://06.8660.org/file/upload/201604/11/1510481429.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 0px; color: transparent; max-width: 600px;\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　肝功能受损的另一大表现则是毛细血管扩张，鼻子布满毛细血管，因此有时&ldquo;红鼻子&rdquo;可能是肝脏出问题的表现。当然，&ldquo;红鼻子&rdquo;也并不一定是肝脏功能下降，而女性在肝脏功能降低，荷尔蒙紊乱时易出现&ldquo;红鼻子&rdquo;。</p>\r\n<p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　5.脸色发黑</p>\r\n<p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　<img src=\"http://06.8660.org/file/upload/201604/11/1510485729.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 0px; color: transparent; max-width: 600px;\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　如果最近发现自己的脸发黑，不一定是晒黑了，也可能是肝脏&ldquo;求救&rdquo;了。肝脏是人体代谢铁元素的重要器官，肝脏功能下降，会导致铁元素无法代谢，在血液中积累，造成脸色发黑。这种现象易发生在男性和绝经后的女性身上。</p>\r\n<p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; word-wrap: break-word; text-indent: 0px;\"><font color=\"#333333\" face=\"宋体\"><span style=\"line-height: 26px;\">文章来源于网络</span></font></p>\r\n<p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; word-wrap: break-word; text-indent: 0px;\"><font color=\"#333333\" face=\"宋体\"><span style=\"line-height: 26px;\">一只特立独行的喵Syca~~~~1163029295@qq.com</span></font></p>');
INSERT INTO `sx_article_data_21` VALUES ('67', ' <p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px; text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://06.8660.org/file/upload/201604/11/1544097429.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 0px; color: transparent; max-width: 600px;\" /></p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px; text-align: center;\"><strong style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">都说中国人的胃太强大</strong></p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px; text-align: center;\"><strong style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">一切外侵生物都能用吃来扫荡解决</strong></p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px; text-align: center;\"><strong style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">但系啊，</strong><strong style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">有些蔬菜，是真的不能吃啊</strong></p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px; text-align: center;\"><strong style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">否则，就会</strong></p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px; text-align: center;\"><strong style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">下辈子！只有！肉！是适合我的！</strong></p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px; text-align: center;\">------------------------------------------------------------------------------------</p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　<span style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">中国胃再强大，也是抵不过毒呀！</span></p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　<span style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">怎样避免吃到这些毒蔬菜呢？他酱这就来给你科普······</span></p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　<strong style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">1.蓝紫色的紫菜</strong></p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　<span style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">紫菜水发后若呈蓝紫色，则说明在海中生长时已被有毒物质环状多肽污染。这些毒素蒸煮也不能解毒，不可食用。</span></p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　<img src=\"http://06.8660.org/file/upload/201604/11/1544098729.png\" alt=\"\" style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 0px; color: transparent; max-width: 600px;\" /></p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　<strong style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">2.四季豆和菜豆</strong></p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　<span style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">四季豆和菜豆的有毒成分主要是皂疳和胰蛋白酶抑制物。烹调时，应先将其煮熟，然后捞出，再加上调味佐料焖煮，便可解毒性。</span></p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　<img src=\"http://06.8660.org/file/upload/201604/11/1544098729.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 0px; color: transparent; max-width: 600px;\" /></p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　<strong style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">3.鲜木耳</strong></p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　<span style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">鲜木耳含有一种琳类光感物质，它对光线敏感，食用后经太阳照射，引起日光皮炎，个别严重的还会因咽喉水肿发生呼吸困难。</span></p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　<img src=\"http://06.8660.org/file/upload/201604/11/1544095029.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 0px; color: transparent; max-width: 600px;\" /></p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　<strong style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">4.新鲜黄花菜</strong></p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　<span style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">所含秋水仙硷进进人体后经氧化会产生有毒物质，食后会引起类似急性肠胃炎症状，极易误诊。而干黄花菜在加工时经净水充分浸泡，已将大部分秋水仙硷溶出，所以一般不会中毒。</span></p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　<img src=\"http://06.8660.org/file/upload/201604/11/1544099429.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 0px; color: transparent; max-width: 600px;\" /></p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　<strong style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">5.蚕豆</strong></p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　<span style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">蚕豆体内红细胞缺乏6-磷酸葡萄糖脱氧酶吃了蚕豆后会得溶血性黄疸，又称蚕豆病。这种病多有遗网传性，因此，有家族病史的人应到医院检查，并避免吃蚕豆。</span></p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　<img src=\"http://06.8660.org/file/upload/201604/11/1544091229.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 0px; color: transparent; max-width: 600px;\" /></p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　<span style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><strong style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">最后的话</strong></span></p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　<span style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">除了以上蔬菜，白果、杏仁、木薯等食用品也都带有一定的毒性，不要过多食用。<br /></span></p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; word-wrap: break-word; text-indent: 0px;\"><font color=\"#333333\" face=\"宋体\"><span style=\"line-height: 26px;\">文章来源于网络</span></font></p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; word-wrap: break-word; text-indent: 0px;\"><font color=\"#333333\" face=\"宋体\"><span style=\"line-height: 26px;\">一只特立独行的喵Syca~~~~1163029295@qq.com</span></font></p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\"><span style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><br type=\"_moz\" /></span></p>');
INSERT INTO `sx_article_data_21` VALUES ('68', ' <span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px;\">　　</span><img src=\"http://06.8660.org/file/upload/201604/11/1608332729.jpeg\" alt=\"\" style=\"font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 0px; color: transparent; max-width: 600px;\" /><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　<span style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">文/王小白 微信：amy_minmin80</span></p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　一份小小的菜单，可以有多少学问？</p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　<span style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">它蕴藏着“多即是少，少既是多”的哲学命题。</span></p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　<span style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">它事关“入口”、“初感、“爆款”等客群沟通的艺术。</span></p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　<span style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">真正有价值的菜单，就是你的商业逻辑，就是你的赚钱武器。</span></p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　<span style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">研究透一份菜单，能让你的餐厅事半功倍。</span></p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　<span style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">｜问题｜</span><span style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">你家有没有让人记住的一道菜？</span></p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　<span style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">事情终究是人的行为，事情的简易、复杂、发展方向都由你来定夺。</span></p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　<span style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">很想问餐饮企业一个最朴实的问题，那就是“你家哪个菜品是消费者一目就了然，一吃就难忘，一听就易记的呢？”</span></p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　<img src=\"http://06.8660.org/file/upload/201604/11/1608331329.jpeg\" alt=\"\" style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 0px; color: transparent; max-width: 600px;\" /></p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　<span style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">假设他第一次来你家，你就能让他记住这一道而已，可以吗？</span></p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　<span style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">我相信有人说可以，而更多人会说，我家很多菜都很可以！</span></p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　<span style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">某心理 ：“一道菜！只推一道菜会让消费者觉得你家难道没有什么好产品了吗？”</span></p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　<span style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">我想说：“一道菜！意在这一道菜，是你家最核心的产品，从原材料到制作到出品到颜值到消费体验，是一道值得被称赞，可圈可点出好之所以然的、并区隔于市面上同类产品的核心产品。”</span></p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　<span style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">｜案例｜</span><span style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">一菜定乾坤</span></p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　<span style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">这里我说一个身边的案例，小钱龙虾，之前一直不怎么发声，后来才发现，真是闷声发大财的感觉！</span></p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　<img src=\"http://06.8660.org/file/upload/201604/11/1608332129.jpeg\" alt=\"\" style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 0px; color: transparent; max-width: 600px;\" /></p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　<span style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">当我们去到他在上海的店，品尝了他家的龙虾，经过一番了解，才发现，他家为什么年年龙虾都生意这么好了！</span></p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　<span style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">其中一个非常核心的原因就在于，有一道几乎桌桌必点的龙虾，而且还是小龙虾！很小很容易入味，而且不是烧、煮的，完全是用洋葱等爆炒出来的，跟我们去到很多龙虾店，什么十三香、咖喱等口味的大龙虾，完全不一样。</span></p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　<span style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">到了夏天，应着街边大排档形式的场景，吃着入口香、脆的小龙虾，那叫一个赶脚真好！据说这一款产品，占营业额的7成。有没有一菜定乾坤的感觉呢？</span></p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　<span style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">｜反思｜</span><span style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">贪多真的好吗？</span></p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　<span style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">讲到这里，很多人说既然这种小龙虾好卖，那我就多做些口味的小龙虾啦！</span></p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　<span style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">这里又想问一个问题！</span></p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　<span style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">如果一张菜单上是各种小龙虾，另一张菜单上只推一款我最有信心、研发最好的小龙虾，其它是几种口味的大龙虾，你会怎么点？</span></p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　<img src=\"http://06.8660.org/file/upload/201604/11/1608334829.jpeg\" alt=\"\" style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 0px; color: transparent; max-width: 600px;\" /></p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　<span style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">这个例子虽然好像是说到了爆款，但我更想表达的是，菜品不在于多，而在于如何定位，如何区隔，如何做到易于在消费者口中传播。</span></p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　<span style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">我相信市面上有很多很多的菜单，一看就有一种不知如何下手的感觉，眼花缭乱，他家什么最好吃呢？我猜、我猜，我使劲儿猜！</span></p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　<span style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">猜对了，吃了感觉还不错，皆大欢喜，猜错了，那就是“什么店啊，这么难吃，撒哟那啦”，也有更甚者，根本没有自己的主打产品，更不用说我的菜单该如何凸显和引导了！消费者到餐厅，点的时候就没有信心，吃的时候就真是看命了。</span></p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　<span style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">｜反思｜顾客几乎不点的菜为什么还留在菜单上</span><span style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">?</span></p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　<span style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">在跟一些餐饮人沟通的时候，看到分类较多，品种繁多的菜品时，我说这里面的菜品有几乎消费者不点的吗？</span></p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　<span style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">然后有的看看数据说，有，或者说有的菜品点的份额接近于零。</span></p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　<span style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">那么小白在想，那你们放在菜单上的意义是什么呢？充品种，看起来更丰富？</span></p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　<img src=\"http://06.8660.org/file/upload/201604/11/1608339329.jpeg\" alt=\"\" style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 0px; color: transparent; max-width: 600px;\" /></p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　<span style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">那么我再问，一道菜的出现，他的备用食材、制作、装盆、服务等等都是一个环节都不能少，你不觉得浪费在没有价值的菜品上本身就是一种浪费吗？</span></p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　<span style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">我相信一份菜单，好有好的道理，差有差的问题。</span></p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　<span style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">｜小结｜</span><span style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">一道菜引发的思考</span></p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　<span style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">一道菜在于认知自己能做到什么！</span></p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　<span style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">一道菜在于清晰自己的产品优势</span></p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　<span style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">并将优势不断放大、扩散；</span></p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　<span style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">清晰核心产品与业态与消费者链接的能力；</span></p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　<span style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">清晰从核心优势出发，做延伸和迭代！</span></p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　<span style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">一道菜，我更是想表达，菜品真的不在于多，</span></p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　<span style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">不要怕做减法，而往往是加法简单，减法难！</span></p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　<span style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">而菜品多的，无疑是对自己的怀疑，根本不知道什么是自己最核心的，最能满足消费者喜好的，才不断的做加法。</span></p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　<span style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">单从菜品上来讲，消费者能记住的，三道菜以内是可以的，而消费者能记住帮你传播一道菜就是你的成功！</span></p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　<strong style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">王小白:</strong></p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　<strong style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">菜单品牌定位设计。从品牌定位、审美学、心理学出发的具有广告思维的菜单美学倡导者，失控餐饮俱乐部联合创始人。</strong></p>');
INSERT INTO `sx_article_data_21` VALUES ('69', '&nbsp;<span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px;\">本文转载自公众号&ldquo;欧洲奶酪&rdquo;</span>\r\n<p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　<span style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">好多朋友发来私信</span><span style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">想知道不同种类的奶酪如何搭配，好在过年的时候做几道&ldquo;重磅&rdquo;西餐~ 贴心的欧欧今天就带大家了解一下</span><strong style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">几种最常见的奶酪该怎么吃~</strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px; text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://06.8660.org/file/upload/201604/11/1637053429.gif\" alt=\"\" style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 0px; color: transparent; max-width: 600px;\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　<span style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">初段的奶酪粉丝能从那些像酸奶味道的新鲜奶酪中找到味觉的乐趣；之后过渡到把硬质奶酪擦碎拌；而进级后就能用口味咸香的花皮软质奶酪和山羊奶酪代替餐后甜点，或者当成看美剧时的小零食了；高手们则钟爱风味独特的洗皮奶酪。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　<span style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">最后，你会爱上重口味的&ldquo;臭奶酪&rdquo;：早餐用蓝纹奶酪配面包，晚餐后饮着红酒吃上一块&hellip;&hellip;每一个阶段，都有独特的乐趣！</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　<img src=\"http://06.8660.org/file/upload/201604/11/1637051329.jpeg\" alt=\"\" style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 0px; color: transparent; max-width: 600px;\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　<span style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">接下来欧欧介绍的是欧洲比较有代表性的几种奶酪和吃法~ 不过，这些搭配 也不是一成不变的，只要不断的尝试和创新，总有一种搭配是最适合自己的。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　<span style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">当舌头恋上奶酪~ 客官请看&darr;&darr;</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　<span style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><strong style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">◆</span></strong></span><span style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><strong style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">希腊羊奶奶酪</span></span></span><span style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">◆</span></span></strong></span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　<span style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">Feta</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　<span style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">原产自希腊的Feta是一种白色盐渍奶酪，传统上是用绵羊奶来制作的不过现在很多地方也采用牛奶来制作。由于Feta奶酪具有比较高的含盐量，因此能够在盐水里存放长达一年，可说已成为羊奶奶酪的代名词。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　<span style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">吃法：</span><span style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">希腊人平日的餐食，从开胃菜、主菜到点心，几乎皆可见Feta奶酪的踪影，著名的希腊沙拉就不能缺少Feta奶酪。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　<img src=\"http://06.8660.org/file/upload/201604/11/1637056029.jpeg\" alt=\"\" style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 0px; color: transparent; max-width: 600px;\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　<span style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><strong style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">◆</span></strong></span><span style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><strong style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">意大利乳清干酪</span></span></span></span><span style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">◆</span></span></strong></span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　<span style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">Ricotta</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　<span style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">柔软，清淡，如同奶油一般湿润而柔滑。风味温和，淡淡的甜味让你很容易爱上它。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　<span style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">吃法：</span><span style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">它是意大利Lasagna等菜肴的传统原料，也是Pizza的重要角色，用来拌沙拉也很好。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　<img src=\"http://06.8660.org/file/upload/201604/11/1637051829.jpeg\" alt=\"\" style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 0px; color: transparent; max-width: 600px;\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　<span style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><strong style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">◆</span></strong></span><span style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><strong style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">水牛奶酪</span></span></span></span></span><span style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">◆</span></span></strong></span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　<span style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">Mozzarella</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　<span style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">表面像瓷器般洁白光滑，柔软而有弹性，味道非常清淡，若有若无的酸，非常温柔的咸，奶香要慢慢品尝才能品味出来。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　<span style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">吃法：</span><span style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">最经典的组合，莫过于切片后和番茄片、罗勒叶一起做成沙拉。Mozzarella还有&ldquo;一口&rdquo;小包装，可以当成零食吃。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　<img src=\"http://06.8660.org/file/upload/201604/11/1637054629.jpeg\" alt=\"\" style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 0px; color: transparent; max-width: 600px;\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　<span style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><strong style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">◆</span></strong></span><span style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><strong style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">帕马森奶酪</span></span></span></span></span></span><span style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">◆</span></span></strong></span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　<span style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">Parmigia o Reggiano</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　<span style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">世界上的顶级奶酪之一，由牛奶制作的硬的干酪非常有陈年的潜力，被称为&ldquo;意大利的乳酪之王&rdquo;。Parmigiano-Reggiano有DOP保护，由其他地方出产或不合格的只可以称为Grana。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　<span style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">吃法：</span><span style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">可以磨成粉状洒在意大利面上或一大块直接佐意大利香醋食用，口感细腻、滑爽。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　<img src=\"http://06.8660.org/file/upload/201604/11/1637059829.jpeg\" alt=\"\" style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 0px; color: transparent; max-width: 600px;\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　<span style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><strong style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">◆</span></strong></span><span style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><strong style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">罗马羊奶酪</span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">◆</span></span></strong></span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　<span style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">Percorino Sardo</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　<span style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">来自意大利罗马的硬质羊奶酪，略有稻草般的色彩，去掉外皮享用里面咸香耐嚼的&ldquo;芯&rdquo;&mdash;&mdash;暗黄色的外壳是不能食用的。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　<span style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">吃法：</span><span style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">将它磨成粉或者削成片放在各种做好的意大利面、海鲜饭上面，然后等它慢慢融化，让食物充分吸收到它的味道。此外，空口当零食吃也是王道！</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　<img src=\"http://06.8660.org/file/upload/201604/11/1637058729.jpeg\" alt=\"\" style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 0px; color: transparent; max-width: 600px;\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　<span style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><strong style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">◆</span></strong></span><span style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><strong style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">新鲜山羊奶酪</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">◆</span></span></strong></span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　<span style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">Goat Cheese</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　<span style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">用山羊奶制成，脂肪含量大大低于用牛奶做的奶酪，而且它还含有大量的维生素A和钾，是节食美女们的最好选择。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　<span style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">吃法：</span><span style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">山羊奶酪遇热很容易融化，因此适合放在意大利面和烩饭上，还可以将加热过的山羊奶酪涂在烤面包上搭配烤蒜一起吃。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　<img src=\"http://06.8660.org/file/upload/201604/11/1637058429.jpeg\" alt=\"\" style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 0px; color: transparent; max-width: 600px;\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　<span style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">好了，奶酪的做法欧欧就给大家介绍到这里了，你学会了吗？快去感受不同奶酪带来的奇妙体验吧~<br />\r\n</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; word-wrap: break-word; text-indent: 0px;\"><font color=\"#333333\" face=\"宋体\"><span style=\"line-height: 26px;\">一只特立独行的喵Syca~~~~1163029295@qq.com</span></font></p>');
INSERT INTO `sx_article_data_21` VALUES ('70', ' <span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px;\">每次说到骂人的最高境，我最佩服的就是嵇康，没错，就是竹林七贤里没事喝喝酒弹弹琴，看上去属于老实人的那位。</span><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　<img src=\"http://06.8660.org/file/upload/201604/11/1721355829.jpeg\" alt=\"\" style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 0px; color: transparent; max-width: 600px;\" /></p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　当初，他朋友山涛邀请他出来做官，触了他的眉头。被他写了一封《与山巨源绝交书》很文艺的喷了一番。大意就是不是针对你啊，我是觉得你们这些世俗礼法都是渣渣。</p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　虽然口吻对山涛还算客气，然而这篇文章却一下火了。几百年读书人都要读不说，几位大书法家还都喜欢临摹一番。刻碑拓帖也多半成了国宝级文物，挂在故宫，让一场文艺青年间的打脸事件以最文艺的方式延续了近两千年。</p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　<img src=\"http://06.8660.org/file/upload/201604/11/1721351229.jpeg\" alt=\"\" style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 0px; color: transparent; max-width: 600px;\" /></p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　所有传世作品中地位最高的属于700年前赵孟頫版，整副作品由行书渐入草书，无论是立意还是造诣都是世所罕见。</p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　而如果说到我自己的本职工作，那葡萄酒领域里最有名的打脸事件，可能要属Bartolo Mascarello酒庄的手绘版“拒绝小桶，拒绝贝鲁斯柯尼”（No Barrique, No Berlusconi）了。</p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　<img src=\"http://06.8660.org/file/upload/201604/11/1721356829.jpeg\" alt=\"\" style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 0px; color: transparent; max-width: 600px;\" /></p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　图片来源：tipicamente.it</p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　这位贝卢斯科尼是意大利最有钱的人之一，意大利最大的媒体大亨，个不高而且花边新闻不断，经常爆出一些让人意想不到的奇怪言论。总的来说，基本上就像本届美国大选的政治谐星唐纳德·川普先生（Do<em></em>nald J. Trump）的意大利版。当然，他两人的相似点还远不止这么多，主要区别是，他真的通过选举成为了二战后在位时间执政最久的总理。这也是为啥不少意大利移民这次都坚定的站在了川普先生共和党的对立面。</p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　<img src=\"http://06.8660.org/file/upload/201604/11/1721351529.jpeg\" alt=\"\" style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 0px; color: transparent; max-width: 600px;\" /></p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　这次大选很多反对川普的人都会吧贝卢斯科尼当成攻击炮弹。</p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　对当年亲手绘制酒标的Bartolo Mascarello老先生来说，贝卢斯科尼和小橡木桶是“发生在意大利最糟糕的两件事了”。所有老先生在世时的手绘酒标都多多少少不太一样。</p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　据他本人描述，第一批酒标的最大特点应该是每张贝鲁斯柯尼的照片外边都有张贴纸，“这样你看厌他的蠢脸之后可以放下来遮住”。在酒庄的巴罗洛就已经一瓶难求的现况下，这款绝版的手绘酒标就更是难得了。几个月前施老师写文章提及此事，立刻有几位大牛在朋友圈把珍贵的藏品晒一番，假如让一个对酒毫不了解的人来看，那恐怕还会以为又是呼应美国大选的政治运动。</p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　<img src=\"http://06.8660.org/file/upload/201604/11/1721354529.jpeg\" alt=\"\" style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 0px; color: transparent; max-width: 600px;\" /></p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　各种版本的拒绝小桶，拒绝贝鲁斯柯尼</p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　如今老先生已经仙逝，贝卢斯科尼倒是还在。随着如今风土理念的复兴，传统风格巴罗洛再度成为全球爱好者追捧名庄的今天。那些珍贵的手绘酒标，以及每一位收藏者对它视若珍宝没事炫耀一下的状态，都仿佛是顽固的老先生当初抗议的延续，增加着对手心理阴影的面积。</p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　<img src=\"http://06.8660.org/file/upload/201604/11/1721351429.jpeg\" alt=\"\" style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 0px; color: transparent; max-width: 600px;\" /></p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　巴托罗在世的时候总自称最后的莫西干人，在如今意大利年轻一代葡萄酒爱好者眼中，他是意大利风土文化教父级的角色。图片来源：wineisterroir.com</p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　其实这类用酒标表达不满的例子还有很多——</p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　波尔多著名的车库酒庄瓦兰德鲁（Château Valandraud），2000年使用防雨布覆盖葡萄园，被判定为违背AOC规定，降级为法国餐酒（Vin de Table Francais）。酒庄为了表达自己很不开心，酒标换成了一双在铁栏杆背后的双手。于是，一款价格超越不少列级名庄，而且有点不开心的餐酒就这样上市了。</p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　<img src=\"http://06.8660.org/file/upload/201604/11/1721353729.jpeg\" alt=\"\" style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 0px; color: transparent; max-width: 600px;\" /></p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　老版本的Valandraud（2012年酒庄升级后更换了新标）和2000年特别版</p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　拥有悠久传统，每年寻找艺术家设计酒标的波尔多名庄木桐古堡（Château Mouton Rothschild）在1993年由巴尔蒂斯（Balthus）创作了一副裸女素描画。因为被美国海关视为“淫秽”，这款酒无法通过审核。为了表示不屑，酒庄并没为了海关需要而设计新的酒标，而是直接用了快空白画取代。由于数量更少，这款特殊版本的酒标甚至比标准版还要受追捧。</p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　<img src=\"http://06.8660.org/file/upload/201604/11/1721351029.jpeg\" alt=\"\" style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 0px; color: transparent; max-width: 600px;\" /></p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　另一个为木桐作画的艺术家，设计1978年酒标的让–保罗·利奥佩尔（Jean-Paul Riopelle）也曾经给他的朋友，勃艮第生产商米库斯基庄园（Domaine Francois Mikulski）一副自己的名画作作为酒标。在他去世后，他的子女向酒庄主收取画作的版权费。而认为友谊被冒犯的庄主直接就着酒瓶上的灰尘画出了新酒标的草稿。由于这款酒标外观特别，每当庄主出席全球各地的品鉴会，几乎都会有人询问酒标背后的故事，而他也很喜欢再重复一遍……</p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　<img src=\"http://06.8660.org/file/upload/201604/11/1721359929.jpeg\" alt=\"\" style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 0px; color: transparent; max-width: 600px;\" /></p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　Francois Mikulski的酒酒标和新酒标</p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　所以说，如果你恰好认识个有点文艺情怀，又恰好爱酒如命的，最好别惹他/她。</p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; word-wrap: break-word; text-indent: 0px;\"><font color=\"#333333\" face=\"宋体\"><span style=\"line-height: 26px;\">　　另外提一句，在用酒标开玩笑的领域，高冷的传统葡萄酒生产国是比不上美国和澳洲人民的脑洞。其中尤以美国人的脑洞最大，这种文化如何形成？这事儿，我们下期讨论。<br /></span></font><strong style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px;\">知味葡萄酒杂志 TasteSpirit.com</strong><br /><font color=\"#333333\" face=\"宋体\"><span style=\"line-height: 26px;\">一只特立独行的喵Syca~~~~1163029295@qq.com</span></font><br /> </p>');
