margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　<span style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">天河区临江大道57号中和广场2层(近珠江新城)</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　<span style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">在越秀区龟岗大马路，白云区云霄路，海珠区滨江西路等有分店。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　<span style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><strong style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">【电话】</span></strong>020-83033588 020-83033688</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　<span style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">3</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　<strong style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">富临食府</strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　<span style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><strong style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">年夜饭火爆程度：★★★★</strong></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　<span style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">地处北京路的旧店，能保持这个价钱 分量 水平，真心很不错。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　<img src=\"http://06.8660.org/file/upload/201604/12/2306575329.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 0px; color: transparent; max-width: 600px;\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　<span style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">招牌菜脆皮猪手，好吃。分量好大，外脆里嫩，肥而不腻。配上芥末酱油，风味独特。价格不用说了，很亲民的价格。年夜饭来这家，性价比很高啊。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　<img src=\"http://06.8660.org/file/upload/201604/12/2306571429.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 0px; color: transparent; max-width: 600px;\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　<span style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><strong style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">【地址】</span></strong>越秀区 惠福东路417号(近教育路)</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　<span style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><strong style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">【电话】</span></strong>020-83302789</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　<span style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">4</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　<span style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">南园酒家</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　<span style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><strong style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">年夜饭火爆程度：★★★★★</strong></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　<span style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">喜欢南园酒家的园林雅致，很有岭南特色，在这里吃年夜饭也是赏心悦目。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　<img src=\"http://06.8660.org/file/upload/201604/12/2306571429.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 0px; color: transparent; max-width: 600px;\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　<span style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">南园市师鸡，鸡肉嫩，碟子里面的汁是珠抽，难得难得。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　<img src=\"http://06.8660.org/file/upload/201604/12/2306579629.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 0px; color: transparent; max-width: 600px;\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　<span style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">