INSERT INTO `sx_article_data_21` VALUES ('77', '&nbsp;<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: inherit; font-size: 1em; text-decoration: inherit; line-height: 25.6px; background-color: rgb(249, 110, 87);\">6家全天候茶楼遍布老城区</span><section class=\"tn-Powered-by-XIUMI\" style=\"margin: 0.8em 0px 0.5em; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px; border: 0px; word-wrap: break-word !im<em></em>portant;\"><section style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !im<em></em>portant; word-wrap: break-word !im<em></em>portant; width: 0px; height: 0px; clear: both;\"></section></section>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px; text-indent: 0px; box-sizing: border-box !im<em></em>portant; word-wrap: break-word !im<em></em>portant;\">木趟栊、满洲窗、大方砖，雕梁画栋、飞檐流苏，位于龙津中路的这栋具有西关大屋特色的建筑，就是沈志辉创立的第一家&ldquo;点都德大茶楼&rdquo;。4年前，父亲沈振伦把两本房产证交给他，让他重新打造一家粤式茶楼，也把振兴广式点心的重任交付给他。经过一年多的筹备，一家传统中透着现代气息的全天候点心茶楼横空出世，新颖的茶点吸引了众多热爱广式早茶的市民。</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px; text-indent: 0px; box-sizing: border-box !im<em></em>portant; word-wrap: break-word !im<em></em>portant;\">&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px; text-indent: 0px; box-sizing: border-box !im<em></em>portant; word-wrap: break-word !im<em></em>portant;\">接过父亲的衣钵前，沈志辉有着自己的事业。他开过奶茶档，也开过快捷酒店，最后，他把经营粤式茶楼当成了终生奋斗的目标。</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px; text-indent: 0px; box-sizing: border-box !im<em></em>portant; word-wrap: break-word !im<em></em>portant;\">&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px; text-indent: 0px; box-sizing: border-box !im<em></em>portant; word-wrap: break-word !im<em></em>portant;\">短短3年间，点都德茶楼连开16家，从荔湾到越秀、天河、海珠，再到进驻珠江新城，到2016年，沈志辉的目标是全市开到30家，全部直营。&ldquo;出品是粤式茶楼的命脉，只有直营才能控制点心的质量。&rdquo;沈志辉说。</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px; text-indent: 0px; box-sizing: border-box !im<em></em>portant; word-wrap: break-word !im<em></em>portant;\">&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px; text-indent: 0px; box-sizing: border-box !im<em></em>portant; word-wrap: break-word !im<em></em>portant;\">&ldquo;&lsquo;一盅两件&rsquo;向来被认为是年长者的生活习惯，但在我看来，传统、怀旧的东西一样可以变得很时尚。&rdquo;在沈志辉的茶楼里，客人可以吃到如虾饺、烧卖、叉烧包等传统茶点，也可以吃到日式青芥三文鱼挞、沙爹金钱肚等新潮点心。而且在点心的卖相上，这里也走时尚路线。&ldquo;我敢说，在这之前，没有一家中式茶楼的点心摆盘能做得如此精致。&rdquo;对于自家茶楼的出品，沈志辉总是满怀信心，每一款茶点的外形、摆盘都经过他的考究。</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px; text-indent: 0px; box-sizing: border-box !im<em></em>portant; word-wrap: break-word !im<em></em>portant; text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://06.8660.org/file/upload/201604/14/1131123626.jpg\" alt=\"QQ截图20160414113426\" width=\"588\" height=\"377\" /><br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n<section class=\"tn-Powered-by-XIUMI\" style=\"margin: 0.8em 0px 0.5em; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px; border: 0px; word-wrap: break-word !im<em></em>portant;\"><span class=\"tn-Powered-by-XIUMI\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0.3em 0.5em; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; word-wrap: break-word !im<em></em>portant; display: inline-block; border-radius: 0.5em; color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 1em; box-shadow: rgb(165, 165, 165) 0.2em 0.2em 0.1em; font-family: inherit; text-decoration: inherit; border-color: rgb(249, 110, 87); background-color: rgb(249, 110, 87);\"><section class=\"tn-Powered-by-XIUMI\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; word-wrap: break-word !im<em></em>portant;\">挑剔老板出品高水准美食</section></span><section style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !im<em></em>portant; word-wrap: break-word !im<em></em>portant; width: 0px; height: 0px; clear: both;\"></section></section>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px; text-indent: 0px; box-sizing: border-box !im<em></em>portant; word-wrap: break-word !im<em></em>portant;\">沈志辉的祖辈、父辈均是饮食行业出身，父母在这个行业里打拼近40年。在沈志辉的记忆里，只有在非常特别的日子才能在家和父母吃一顿饭，而这些&ldquo;特别的日子&rdquo;一年里几乎不会超过一个星期，当中包括了大年初一等重大的节庆日子。&ldquo;没办法，做餐饮行业的人，别人最闲的时候，就是他们最忙的时候。&rdquo;沈志辉称，即使是现在，茶楼已经交由他来打理，父亲依然坚持每天5点起床出门帮忙打理生意，晚上11点才回到家。</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px; text-indent: 0px; box-sizing: border-box !im<em></em>portant; word-wrap: break-word !im<em></em>portant; text-align: center;\"><img data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-src=\"http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz/s98YFME3l93sCACk848vMtGNqWcicHSsO05NibibqQ5UJKdrcNXaUdB6aFKeOIvAwJjloZLnXGLu8zFPdIDq99bPg/0?wx_fmt=png\" data-ratio=\"0.6690647482014388\" data-w=\"\" src=\"http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz/s98YFME3l93sCACk848vMtGNqWcicHSsO05NibibqQ5UJKdrcNXaUdB6aFKeOIvAwJjloZLnXGLu8zFPdIDq99bPg/640?wx_fmt=png&amp;tp=webp&amp;wxfrom=5&amp;wx_lazy=1\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; height: auto !im<em></em>portant; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !im<em></em>portant; word-wrap: break-word !im<em></em>portant; width: auto !im<em></em>portant; visibility: visible !im<em></em>portant;\" alt=\"\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px; text-indent: 0px; box-sizing: border-box !im<em></em>portant; word-wrap: break-word !im<em></em>portant;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !im<em></em>portant; word-wrap: break-word !im<em></em>portant; color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">茶楼里的每一款茶点，都经过沈志辉细致的考究。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px; text-indent: 0px; box-sizing: border-box !im<em></em>portant; word-wrap: break-word !im<em></em>portant;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px; text-indent: 0px; box-sizing: border-box !im<em></em>portant; word-wrap: break-word !im<em></em>portant;\">从小到大吃不上&ldquo;住家饭&rdquo;的沈志辉养成了独立自主的性格和喜欢下馆子尝试美食的习惯。不过，沈志辉直言，别人下馆子只注重于食物的味道，而他却关注于食物的品质是否有提升的空间，&ldquo;品尝美食本应该是一种享受，对于我来说，却又成了一种挑剔的习惯。所以，现在吃东西也成了一种苦恼。&rdquo;也正是由于沈志辉的这种挑剔，才让他的点心经受住了那么多&ldquo;嘴刁&rdquo;食客的考验。</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px; text-indent: 0px; box-sizing: border-box !im<em></em>portant; word-wrap: break-word !im<em></em>portant;\">&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px; text-indent: 0px; box-sizing: border-box !im<em></em>portant; word-wrap: break-word !im<em></em>portant;\">和父辈的经营理念不同，作为80后老板的沈志辉不再只顾低头盯着材料采购、菜品品质等&ldquo;硬件&rdquo;建设，对于茶楼的经营模式管理、网上推广等&ldquo;软件&rdquo;的建设，沈志辉同样不放松。&ldquo;我每时每刻在思考客人需要些什么，什么样的服务能够满足他们的需求，包括结账方式、餐位设置、食物的性价比等等。&rdquo; 沈志辉说。</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px; text-indent: 0px; box-sizing: border-box !im<em></em>portant; word-wrap: break-word !im<em></em>portant;\">沈志辉开在老城区的茶楼坚持每天早上7点营业，晚上10点才收市，每天做足15个小时。&ldquo;对于老一辈的广州人而言，一天的时间是从早上5点半开始的。年纪大了，容易早醒，运动了一圈，买份报纸，就等茶楼开市叹个一盅两件。早点开市，能让他们有个地方落脚。&rdquo;沈志辉说，这也是坚守传统的一种方式，实际上，早上9点前茶市并不赚钱，&ldquo;我们赚的是口碑。&rdquo;</p>\r\n<section class=\"tn-Powered-by-XIUMI\" style=\"margin: 0.8em 0px 0.5em; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px; border: 0px; word-wrap: break-word !im<em></em>portant;\"><span class=\"tn-Powered-by-XIUMI\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0.3em 0.5em; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; word-wrap: break-word !im<em></em>portant; display: inline-block; border-radius: 0.5em; color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 1em; box-shadow: rgb(165, 165, 165) 0.2em 0.2em 0.1em; font-family: inherit; text-decoration: inherit; border-color: rgb(249, 110, 87); background-color: rgb(249, 110, 87);\"><section class=\"tn-Powered-by-XIUMI\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; word-wrap: break-word !im<em></em>portant;\">关注点心之外也关心公益慈善</section></span><section style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !im<em></em>portant; word-wrap: break-word !im<em></em>portant; width: 0px; height: 0px; clear: both;\"></section></section>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px; text-indent: 0px; box-sizing: border-box !im<em></em>portant; word-wrap: break-word !im<em></em>portant;\">在沈志辉看来，一盅两件最能代表&ldquo;食在广州&rdquo;，外地人了解粤菜大多是从点心开始。为此，他专门在北京北路的分店筹集一处点心博物馆，推广广府点心文化，并计划逐步把广府民间工艺引入茶楼。</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px; text-indent: 0px; box-sizing: border-box !im<em></em>portant; word-wrap: break-word !im<em></em>portant;\">&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px; text-indent: 0px; box-sizing: border-box !im<em></em>portant; word-wrap: break-word !im<em></em>portant;\">工作之外，沈志辉还是广东狮子会阳光天使的成员，也是一名优秀义工。从2015年1月起，沈志辉与广州市义工联联合发起成立广州市首个&ldquo;爱心代餐日&rdquo;，每个月第三个星期四，所有门店为社区困难人士提供不少于100份爱心代餐，由义工分发给社区弱势群体。&ldquo;我们更希望能搭建起这个平台，以点带面，带动公益慈善，让不同企业加入其中。沈志辉说，&ldquo;我承诺，只要有点都德一天，都会坚持派发爱心早餐。&rdquo;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px; text-indent: 0px; box-sizing: border-box !im<em></em>portant; word-wrap: break-word !im<em></em>portant;\">&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px; text-indent: 0px; box-sizing: border-box !im<em></em>portant; word-wrap: break-word !im<em></em>portant;\">在企业管理中，沈志辉也会发动员工去做公益慈善，到如今，公益已经成为他的企业文化的一部分。&ldquo;通过做公益的方式，让年轻员工去见识社会的另一面。让他们懂得，其实能够靠双手自主谋取生活已经很幸福，在我们的社区帮扶对象中，有些人连劳动力都没有。&rdquo;沈志辉说，施比受更有福，能为他人付出也应该感恩。<br />\r\n<span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); line-height: 22.4px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(250, 250, 239);\">好人说：&ldquo;广式点心吃的不仅是美味，更是一种情怀。做点心也如此，既要继承传统、突破传统，也要守住广式点心之魂。<br />\r\n</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px; text-indent: 0px; box-sizing: border-box !im<em></em>portant; word-wrap: break-word !im<em></em>portant;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !im<em></em>portant; word-wrap: break-word !im<em></em>portant; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 14px;\">内容来源信息时报<br />\r\n<br />\r\n</span></p>');
INSERT INTO `sx_article_data_21` VALUES ('78', ' 导语：<span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px;\">每个女人都爱美，每天照着镜子梳洗打扮，抹化妆品是皮肤表面的护理，想从里到外的容光焕发，还得从美食着手；有句老话，日吃三枣，终身不老，不无道理；红枣富含维生素C，补血养颜之佳品，食用比较方便；单吃红枣有时候想不起来，做主食一举两得，真心不错，女人吃出好气色，请朋友们随米兰看看红枣包的具体做法。</span><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　<img src=\"http://06.8660.org/file/upload/201604/14/2258406226.jpeg\" alt=\"\" style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 0px; color: transparent; max-width: 600px;\" /></p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　<span style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">准备食材：中筋面粉460克，酵母3克，清水250毫升；大红枣适量。红枣洗净，晾干最好没有水滴备用。清水可以改成牛奶随意就好。 每一步制作步骤都很详细哦。</span></p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　<img src=\"http://06.8660.org/file/upload/201604/14/2258404026.jpeg\" alt=\"\" style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 0px; color: transparent; max-width: 600px;\" /></p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　<span style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">面粉放入盆中，取清水放入酵母化开后，慢慢加入面粉中，揉成面团；水一定慢慢加入，不要一下子全部倒入，揉好的面团做到三光，盆光，面光，手光；用屉布盖上发酵1个半小时左右，是原来的一倍大即可。</span></p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　<img src=\"http://06.8660.org/file/upload/201604/14/2258405926.jpeg\" alt=\"\" style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 0px; color: transparent; max-width: 600px;\" /></p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　<span style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">面团发好后切开揉成一长条，大约直径4厘米左右，再切分成一个个小面剂子，大枣比较大，所以剂子不要太大，正好包裹一个大枣就行了。</span></p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　<img src=\"http://06.8660.org/file/upload/201604/14/2258403126.jpeg\" alt=\"\" style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 0px; color: transparent; max-width: 600px;\" /></p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　<span style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">小面剂子擀开放入一个大枣，包成类似饺子形状，不封口。全部包好后上屉。</span></p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　<img src=\"http://06.8660.org/file/upload/201604/14/2258409326.jpeg\" alt=\"\" style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 0px; color: transparent; max-width: 600px;\" /></p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　<span style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">凉水做锅，篦子上放上屉布，摆上红枣包，醒发20分钟。</span></p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　<img src=\"http://06.8660.org/file/upload/201604/14/2258402326.jpeg\" alt=\"\" style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 0px; color: transparent; max-width: 600px;\" /></p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　<span style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">点火等锅开后，转为中火，开始计时，15分钟关火，焖上5分钟揭锅开盖，很重要一定记住了。红枣蒸熟后比生吃味道好。</span></p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　<img src=\"http://06.8660.org/file/upload/201604/14/2258404726.jpeg\" alt=\"\" style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 0px; color: transparent; max-width: 600px;\" /></p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; word-wrap: break-word; text-indent: 0px;\"><font color=\"#333333\" face=\"宋体\"><span style=\"line-height: 26px;\">　　</span></font><span style=\"border: 0px; border-image-source: initial; border-image-slice: initial; border-image-width: initial; border-image-outset: initial; border-image-repeat: initial; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><font color=\"#333333\" face=\"宋体\"><span style=\"line-height: 26px;\">蒸好的红枣包甜软可口，一口咬下去就是枣肉，很满足，早餐吃两个红枣包富于营养容易吸收养颜补血。</span></font><br /><font color=\"#333333\" face=\"宋体\"><span style=\"line-height: 26px;\">图片来源于网络</span></font><br /><font color=\"#333333\" face=\"宋体\"><span style=\"line-height: 26px;\">一只特立独行的喵Syca</span></font></span></p>');
INSERT INTO `sx_article_data_21` VALUES ('79', '&nbsp;<span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px;\">天辣噜，葡萄酒竟然还有这些隐藏技能？GET了这些，妈妈再也不用担心我的&hellip;&hellip;妈妈什么都不用担心了！</span>\r\n<p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　<img img_width=\"600\" img_height=\"338\" src=\"http://06.8660.org/file/upload/201604/14/2329107026.gif\" alt=\"\" style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 0px; color: transparent; max-width: 600px;\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　<span style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">没喝完</span>的葡萄酒&nbsp;<span style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">又</span>来放大招咯</p>\r\n<p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　<span style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">NO.1 红酒煮鸡蛋可以预防感冒</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　做法So Easy!把适量红酒倒入小锅中煮开，让酒精随蒸汽挥发干净，然后打入鸡蛋，稍加搅动后停止加热，来点儿白糖调味，趁热一口气喝下。一觉醒来，从此感冒是路人。</p>\r\n<p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　姑娘们注意了：此方还能缓解痛经，每个月的那几天记得试试</p>\r\n<p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　<span style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">NO.2&nbsp;</span><span style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">清洗蔬菜水果时加点儿葡萄酒，干净又好吃</span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　葡萄酒可谓是100%纯天然绿色清洗剂&mdash;&mdash;其中的酒精能溶解蔬果表面杂质，其他成分还能杀灭大肠杆菌、沙门氏菌等细菌。另外，葡萄酒洗过的蔬果还会更加美味。</p>\r\n<p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　<img img_width=\"640\" img_height=\"426\" src=\"http://06.8660.org/file/upload/201604/14/2329102326.jpeg\" alt=\"\" style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 0px; color: transparent; max-width: 600px;\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　<span style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">NO.3&nbsp;</span><span style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">自制浓汤宝</span></span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　将没喝完的葡萄酒倒入冰格中冻成小冰块，做汤或炖肉时，取一两块做调料，会有菜鸟变大厨的奇效。</p>\r\n<p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　<span style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">NO.4&nbsp;</span><span style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">白葡萄酒可去除红酒渍</span></span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　红酒渍还在你的衣服上撒野？白葡萄酒闻讯赶来&ldquo;以毒攻毒&rdquo;。衣服、地毯等沾染上红酒渍后，立刻倒些白葡萄酒，等浸透后用毛巾擦净即可。</p>\r\n<p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　白葡萄酒谦虚地告诉小雅：其实去除汽油渍也不在话下。</p>\r\n<p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　<img img_width=\"600\" img_height=\"400\" src=\"http://06.8660.org/file/upload/201604/14/2329107126.jpeg\" alt=\"\" style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 0px; color: transparent; max-width: 600px;\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　<span style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">NO.5&nbsp;</span><span style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">保温壶御用除味剂</span></span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　保温壶用久了水就容易变味。加一小勺红葡萄酒，倒入干净的水泡一天，冲洗干净后再装水就和新的一样了。</p>\r\n<p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　您的好友洗涤剂同学表示鸭梨很大。</p>\r\n<p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　<span style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">NO.6&nbsp;</span><span style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">煎鱼前，向锅里喷小半杯白葡萄酒，能防止鱼皮粘锅。</span></span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　防粘锅技能Plus：干煸蔬菜时加点干白葡萄酒，同样起到防粘锅效果，尤其适用于炒洋葱。</p>\r\n<p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　<img img_width=\"640\" img_height=\"426\" src=\"http://06.8660.org/file/upload/201604/14/2329107126.jpeg\" alt=\"\" style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 0px; color: transparent; max-width: 600px;\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　<span style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">NO.7&nbsp;</span><span style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">去除鱼类和肉类的不和谐味道</span></span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　炖鱼煎鱼加点儿葡萄酒，去腥提鲜；涮羊肉时向火锅里倒点儿葡萄酒，羊膻味再见。</p>\r\n<p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　<span style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">NO.8&nbsp;</span><span style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">用白葡萄酒擦玻璃，倍儿亮</span></span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　近日，白葡萄酒于发布会中表示：&ldquo;就是有实力把你家玻璃变得像没装玻璃一样。&rdquo;几勺白葡萄酒，用适量水稀释，加入喷壶中喷到玻璃上，用抹布一擦&hellip;&hellip;见证奇迹的时刻！</p>\r\n<p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　当然，镜子，炉台，厨具也可以用此妙招。</p>\r\n<p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　P.s. 白葡萄酒和花岗岩不约不约哦，因为白葡萄酒中的酸会将花岗岩腐蚀。</p>\r\n<p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　<img img_width=\"640\" img_height=\"374\" src=\"http://06.8660.org/file/upload/201604/14/2329106826.jpeg\" alt=\"\" style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 0px; color: transparent; max-width: 600px;\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　<span style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">NO.9&nbsp;</span><span style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">看起来年轻十岁的秘密武器</span></span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　红酒富含抗氧化物，可柔化肌肤，减少皱纹，让肌肤更有活力。喝不完的红酒用来洗澡，或者当做爽肤水擦在脸上，能使皮肤嫩滑细腻。</p>\r\n<p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　注意：葡萄酒中含酒精，过敏者慎用。</p>\r\n<p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　<span style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">NO.10&nbsp;</span><span style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">拌馅加酒，越吃越有</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　拌饺子、包子馅时加入适量干白葡萄酒，馅不易散开，皮也不容易破，美味程度连胜三级！</p>\r\n<p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　<img img_width=\"640\" img_height=\"427\" src=\"http://06.8660.org/file/upload/201604/14/2329102726.jpeg\" alt=\"\" style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 0px; color: transparent; max-width: 600px;\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; word-wrap: break-word; text-indent: 0px;\"><font color=\"#333333\" face=\"宋体\"><span style=\"line-height: 26px;\">　　经鉴定，wuli葡萄酒除能出色完成本职工作外，在</span></font><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; border: 0px; border-image-source: initial; border-image-slice: initial; border-image-width: initial; border-image-outset: initial; border-image-repeat: initial; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">养生</span><font color=\"#333333\" face=\"宋体\"><span style=\"line-height: 26px;\">、</span></font><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; border: 0px; border-image-source: initial; border-image-slice: initial; border-image-width: initial; border-image-outset: initial; border-image-repeat: initial; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">清洁</span><font color=\"#333333\" face=\"宋体\"><span style=\"line-height: 26px;\">、</span></font><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; border: 0px; border-image-source: initial; border-image-slice: initial; border-image-width: initial; border-image-outset: initial; border-image-repeat: initial; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">烹饪</span><font color=\"#333333\" face=\"宋体\"><span style=\"line-height: 26px;\">，</span></font><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; border: 0px; border-image-source: initial; border-image-slice: initial; border-image-width: initial; border-image-outset: initial; border-image-repeat: initial; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">美容</span><font color=\"#333333\" face=\"宋体\"><span style=\"line-height: 26px;\">等方面均有不俗表现。</span></font><br />\r\n<font color=\"#333333\" face=\"宋体\"><span style=\"line-height: 26px;\">图片来源于网络</span></font><br />\r\n<font color=\"#333333\" face=\"宋体\"><span style=\"line-height: 26px;\">一只特立独行的喵Syca~~~~1163029295@qq.com</span></font><br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>');
INSERT INTO `sx_article_data_21` VALUES ('80', '&nbsp;<strong style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">红薯叶？</strong>\r\n<p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\"><span style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">只听过红薯可以吃啊！<br />\r\n没错！今天要说的，</span><br />\r\n<span style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">就是一直被大家彻底忽视的&ldquo;蔬菜皇后&rdquo;</span><br />\r\n<span style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">&mdash;&mdash;红薯叶。</span><br />\r\n<span style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">红薯好吃，红薯叶当然也不赖~</span><br />\r\n<span style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">告诉你们吧，红薯叶当真是个宝呢！</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　<img src=\"http://06.8660.org/file/upload/201604/14/2346188626.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 0px; color: transparent; max-width: 600px;\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　<strong style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">红薯叶的营养价值<br />\r\n</strong>1排毒<br />\r\n<span style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">含丰富叶绿素，能够&ldquo;净化血液&rdquo;，帮助排毒。</span><br />\r\n2提高免疫力<br />\r\n<span style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">含有比一般蔬菜高5～10倍的抗氧化物，能提高免疫力，&ldquo;预防感冒&rdquo;。</span><br />\r\n3预防贫血<br />\r\n<span style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">每天摄取300g的地瓜叶，就可补充人体一天所需的铁质及维生素A、C、E。</span><br />\r\n4预防高血压<br />\r\n<span style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">富含钾，有助血压控制，预防高血压。</span><br />\r\n5改善便秘<br />\r\n<span style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">丰富的膳食纤维，可促进肠胃蠕动，预防&ldquo;便秘及痔疮&rdquo;。</span><br />\r\n6改善更年期症状<br />\r\n<span style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">富含植固醇，可以达到与荷尔蒙类似的调节身体机能的功效。</span><br />\r\n7促进乳汁分泌<br />\r\n<span style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">含有黄酮类化合物等物质，能促进乳汁分泌。</span><br />\r\n8强化视力<br />\r\n<span style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">有丰富维生素A，可强化视力。<br />\r\n</span><br />\r\n<strong style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">红薯叶菜谱</strong><span style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><strong style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><em style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">1</em></strong></span>凉拌红薯叶</p>\r\n<p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　<strong style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><img src=\"http://06.8660.org/file/upload/201604/14/2346187726.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 0px; color: transparent; max-width: 600px;\" /></strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　<strong style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">材料：</strong><span style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">嫩红薯叶400克，大蒜30克，素油15毫升，精盐、黄酒、味精、鲜汤、麻油各适量。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　<span style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><strong style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">做法：</strong></span><br />\r\n<span style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">1.将嫩红薯叶茎洗净，放入沸水锅中焯后捞出用凉水冲凉，切成段。大蒜剥皮捣成茸。</span><br />\r\n<span style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">2.炒锅置火上，放素油烧至四成热，放人大蒜茸炒出香味，加入嫩红薯叶茎翻炒，加入鲜汤、精盐、黄酒炒入味，加入味精、麻油，撒上剩余的蒜茸拌匀即成。</span><br />\r\n<span style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><br />\r\n<strong style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><em style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">2</em></strong></span>蒜蓉红薯叶</p>\r\n<p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　<strong style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><img src=\"http://06.8660.org/file/upload/201604/14/2346181426.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 0px; color: transparent; max-width: 600px;\" /></strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　<strong style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">材料：</strong><span style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">红薯叶500克， 大蒜30克，油适量，鸡精适量</span><br />\r\n<span style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><strong style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">做法：</strong></span><br />\r\n<span style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">1、起油锅，放蒜爆香，放入红薯叶快炒至熟，加入鸡精和盐调味再拌匀即可起锅。</span><br />\r\n<span style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">用红薯叶+橄榄油一茶匙这样的炒法可以起到美容瘦身的效果哦！</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\"><span style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><strong style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><em style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">3&nbsp;</em></strong></span>虾仁红薯叶鸡汤</p>\r\n<p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　<strong style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><img src=\"http://06.8660.org/file/upload/201604/14/2346185226.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 0px; color: transparent; max-width: 600px;\" /></strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　<strong style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">材料：</strong><span style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">红薯叶、虾仁、蘑菇、鸡汤、盐、胡椒粉、鸡精、香油</span><br />\r\n<span style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><strong style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">做法：</strong></span><br />\r\n<span style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">1.红薯叶去掉叶柄，洗净；虾仁除去沙线，洗净；蘑菇去根，洗净。</span><br />\r\n<span style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">2.虾仁、红薯叶分别焯水。</span><br />\r\n<span style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">3.虾仁、蘑菇、红薯叶放鸡汤中，加盐、料酒、胡椒粉、鸡精，大火烧沸，小火煮5分钟。</span><br />\r\n<span style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">4.出锅装碗，淋上香油，ok。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\"><span style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><strong style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><em style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">4&nbsp;</em></strong></span>红薯叶饼</p>\r\n<p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　<strong style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><img src=\"http://06.8660.org/file/upload/201604/14/2346188726.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 0px; color: transparent; max-width: 600px;\" /></strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　<strong style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">材料：</strong><span style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">红薯叶小把、鸡蛋2个、白面粉少许、玉少许、米面少许、盐少许、香油少许、小苏打</span><br />\r\n<span style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><strong style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">做法：</strong></span><br />\r\n<span style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">1.红薯叶洗净，过开水备用。</span><br />\r\n<span style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">2.将焯好的红薯叶放入凉水中过一下。</span><br />\r\n<span style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">3.挤干水分切末，取一大碗，加入白面粉和玉米面、鸡蛋、小苏打、盐。</span><br />\r\n<span style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">4.加入少许水搅拌成糊状备用。</span><br />\r\n<span style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">5.饼铛预热后刷上香油，将面糊用勺子淋入饼铛上煎至两面金黄即可。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\"><span style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><strong style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><em style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">5&nbsp;</em></strong></span>虾米辣椒红薯叶</p>\r\n<p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　<strong style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><img src=\"http://06.8660.org/file/upload/201604/14/2346186326.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 0px; color: transparent; max-width: 600px;\" /></strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　<strong style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">材料：</strong><span style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">红薯叶、食油、蒜蓉、虾米碎、红辣椒（切圈圈）、酱清</span><br />\r\n<span style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><strong style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">做法：</strong></span><br />\r\n<span style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">1、洗净番薯叶及叶梗撕弃刃丝控干水。</span><br />\r\n<span style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">2、热油爆香虾米蒜蓉。</span><br />\r\n<span style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">3、投入番薯叶梗和辣椒圈圈旺火翻炒一炒随即倒入叶片速炒1分钟熄火。</span><br />\r\n<span style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">4、淋少许酱清提味。<br />\r\n</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\"><b><i>6&nbsp;</i></b>红薯叶馒头</p>\r\n<p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　<strong style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><img src=\"http://06.8660.org/file/upload/201604/14/2346187826.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 0px; color: transparent; max-width: 600px;\" /></strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　<strong style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">材料:</strong><span style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">红薯叶、瓣蒜4-5个、盐、生抽、香油、水</span><br />\r\n<strong style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">做法:</strong><br />\r\n<span style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">1.红薯叶馒头：红薯叶洗净控水，切碎（不用特别碎，用刀来回切几下就好），放入发好的面盆中，加少许盐，一起揉进面中。</span><br />\r\n<span style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">2.然后分成小块面揉成窝窝头状，放进温水锅里，醒发30分钟左右。</span><br />\r\n<span style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">3.然后大火开始蒸，水开后改中小火蒸25分钟即可。</span><br />\r\n<span style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">4.蒜汁：4-5瓣蒜，用压蒜器压成蒜泥，加生抽、香油、少许盐、一点儿凉白开兑开。</span><br />\r\n<b><i>7 &nbsp;</i></b>蒸红薯叶</p>\r\n<p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　<strong style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><img src=\"http://06.8660.org/file/upload/201604/14/2346188226.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 0px; color: transparent; max-width: 600px;\" /></strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　<strong style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">材料：</strong><span style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">红薯叶、面粉、麻油、蒜汁、盐味、辣油</span><br />\r\n<strong style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">做法：<br />\r\n</strong><span style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">1.把择好的红薯叶洗干净，稍微控水。</span><br />\r\n<span style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">2.加入面粉拌均。</span><br />\r\n<span style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">3.把拌发的红薯叶上笼蒸熟。</span><br />\r\n<span style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">4.把蒸熟的红薯叶稍冷却5分种。</span><br />\r\n<span style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">5.加入麻油、蒜汁、盐味、辣油各适量，拌匀出盘即可。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\"><span style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">其实，红薯叶就像青菜一样</span><br />\r\n<span style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">做法相似，口感也差不多</span><br />\r\n<span style=\"border: 0px; border-image-source: initial; border-image-slice: initial; border-image-width: initial; border-image-outset: initial; border-image-repeat: initial; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><font color=\"#333333\" face=\"宋体\"><span style=\"line-height: 26px;\">真替它这么多年被冷落叫屈！</span></font><br />\r\n<font color=\"#333333\" face=\"宋体\"><span style=\"line-height: 26px;\">图片来源于网络</span></font><br />\r\n<font color=\"#333333\" face=\"宋体\"><span style=\"line-height: 26px;\">一只特立独行的喵Syca</span></font></span></p>');
INSERT INTO `sx_article_data_21` VALUES ('81', '&nbsp;<img src=\"http://06.8660.org/file/upload/201604/16/1606558826.jpg\" alt=\"\" />\r\n<div class=\"c_jianjie cbox\" style=\"margin: 0px auto 15px; padding: 0px; clear: both; overflow: auto; color: rgb(52, 52, 52); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, Tahoma, 宋体; line-height: 24px;\">\r\n<h2 style=\"margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 18.2px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">热红酒的简介及特色</h2>\r\n葡萄第一次喝热红酒，是在冰天雪地的布拉格圣诞集市上。那一年的冬天格外冷，布拉格肯定是当仁不让的。傍晚的时候，我和婆婆还有史先生从酒店出来，去寻找食物的途中，实在敌不过严寒，俺和婆婆就赶紧要了两杯热红酒。第一口的感觉，真甜！第二口，有些酒味儿了，第三口，嘿，这酒还挺有劲儿的哈！恩，如果要我描述滴更加生动一些得话，就是－－喝了热红酒，全身上下沸腾起来～<br />\r\n分类标签：<span style=\"background-color: rgb(128, 0, 0);\">时尚饮品 &nbsp;延缓衰老食谱 美容食谱</span><br />\r\n菜品口味：<span style=\"background-color: rgb(128, 0, 0);\">香味</span> &nbsp;主要工艺：<span style=\"background-color: rgb(128, 0, 0);\">煮</span><br />\r\n所需时间 ：<span style=\"background-color: rgb(128, 0, 0);\">10-30分钟</span> &nbsp; 制作难度：<span style=\"background-color: rgb(128, 0, 0);\">简单</span><br />\r\n食材明细：<span style=\"background-color: rgb(128, 0, 0);\">红酒 &nbsp;白糖或红糖 &nbsp;新鲜橙皮 &nbsp;丁香 &nbsp;肉桂</span>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class=\"cbox\" style=\"margin: 0px auto 15px; padding: 0px; clear: both; overflow: auto; color: rgb(52, 52, 52); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, Tahoma, 宋体; line-height: 24px;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class=\"c_buzhou cbox\" style=\"margin: 0px auto 15px; padding: 0px; clear: both; overflow: auto; color: rgb(52, 52, 52); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, Tahoma, 宋体; line-height: 24px;\">\r\n<h2 style=\"margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 18.2px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">热红酒的做法详细步骤<br />\r\n<span class=\"c_bz_num\" style=\"line-height: 24px; margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\">1、</span><span style=\"color: rgb(52, 52, 52); line-height: 24px;\">将适量红酒倒入锅内，同时将肉桂，丁香，和橙子皮，以及红糖一起放入；（我个人偏爱用红糖）<br />\r\n</span><span class=\"c_bz_num\" style=\"line-height: 24px; margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\">2、</span><span style=\"color: rgb(52, 52, 52); line-height: 24px;\">用最小的火，将锅子慢慢烧热；同时也用勺子将红酒和糖等均匀的搅拌开；<br />\r\n</span><span class=\"c_bz_num\" style=\"line-height: 24px; margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\">3、</span><span style=\"color: rgb(52, 52, 52); line-height: 24px;\">大约待到能闻到红酒的热香，并能看到红酒冒出的热气后，依旧保持最小火，继续搅拌，直至糖融化，同时也可以使得肉桂，丁香和橙皮的味道渗入的更侬些；<br />\r\n</span><span class=\"c_bz_num\" style=\"line-height: 24px; margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\">4、</span><span style=\"color: rgb(52, 52, 52); line-height: 24px;\">大约熬个10－15分钟就可以关火，倒入杯中，成趁热饮用了。</span></h2>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"c_tieshi cbox\" style=\"margin: 0px auto 15px; padding: 0px; clear: both; overflow: auto; color: rgb(52, 52, 52); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, Tahoma, 宋体; line-height: 24px;\">\r\n<h2 style=\"margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 18.2px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">热红酒的做法小贴士</h2>\r\n注意：在整个热红酒的过程中，都要保持最小火力，千万不要将红酒煮沸腾了。</div>\r\n图片来源于网络<br />\r\n一只特立独行的喵Syca~~~~<br type=\"_moz\" />');
INSERT INTO `sx_article_data_21` VALUES ('82', ' <strong style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">酸奶苹果面包</strong><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　<img src=\"http://06.8660.org/file/upload/201604/16/1613135626.jpg\" style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 0px; color: transparent; max-width: 650px;\" alt=\"\" /></p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px; text-align: center;\"><strong style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">风靡酸奶杯</strong></p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　<img src=\"http://06.8660.org/file/upload/201604/16/1613133926.jpg\" style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 0px; color: transparent; max-width: 650px;\" alt=\"\" /></p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px; text-align: center;\">简简单单的酸奶木糠</p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　<img src=\"http://06.8660.org/file/upload/201604/16/1613136926.jpg\" style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 0px; color: transparent; max-width: 650px;\" alt=\"\" /></p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　嘿嘿，酸奶不单止可以吃</p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　告诉你的一秘密酸奶还可以直接敷脸</p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px; text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://06.8660.org/file/upload/201604/16/1613131326.jpg\" style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 0px; color: transparent; max-width: 650px;\" alt=\"\" /></p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　酸奶可以补充脸部营养，滋润皮肤，有一定的美白效果，长时间要坚持可以达到很好改善肌肤的效果效果非常明显。</p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　酸奶敷脸步骤:</p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　1.首先先清洁脸部，先用热水扑面，让脸部毛孔张开，挤出适量洗面奶抹上，揉搓之后洗净，再用温水洗脸，让毛孔慢慢收缩。</p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　2.把酸奶均匀的涂在面部，躺在床上，可以闭目养神，但是不能笑，笑是做面膜的大忌，做面膜时笑更容易长皱纹，一周一次即可。</p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　3.15-20分钟后，用温水轻轻的将酸奶洗掉即可。</p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　<strong style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">注意事项</strong></p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　酸奶敷脸适合肌肤：<strong style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">中性和干性</strong></p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　干性肌肤可以用酸奶补充脸部营养，滋润皮肤。如果是油性肌肤，就可能会产生脂肪粒和疙瘩，所以酸奶面膜是比较适合中性和干性肌肤。</p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　酸奶多样化吃法</p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　喜欢怎么吃就怎么吃吧！</p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　吃不完还可以敷脸万能的健康美容品</p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px; text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://06.8660.org/file/upload/201604/16/1613138626.jpg\" style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 0px; color: transparent; max-width: 650px;\" alt=\"\" /></p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　在家制作酸奶很简单轻轻松松搞点：</p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　材料：</p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　纯牛奶 750ml、乳酸菌 1包、细砂糖 适量</p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　1：准备材料</p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　2：将250ml的牛奶倒入酸奶锅里，加入乳酸菌，边加边搅拌均匀（搅几分钟）</p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px; text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://06.8660.org/file/upload/201604/16/1613135126.png\" style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 0px; color: transparent; max-width: 650px;\" alt=\"\" /></p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　3：加入适量细砂糖，搅拌至糖融化</p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　4：再加入剩下的500ml牛奶，继续搅拌均匀</p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px; text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://06.8660.org/file/upload/201604/16/1613138526.png\" style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 0px; color: transparent; max-width: 650px;\" alt=\"\" /></p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　5：现在的天气有点凉，要在酸奶机里倒入适量的热水（热水无需太热）</p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　6：将牛奶放入酸奶机盖上盖子通电8小时左右就好了</p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px; text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://06.8660.org/file/upload/201604/16/1613137526.png\" style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 0px; color: transparent; max-width: 650px;\" alt=\"\" /></p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　7：做好的酸奶放入冰箱冷藏，凝固就可以开吃啦</p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px; text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://06.8660.org/file/upload/201604/16/1613137926.jpg\" style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 0px; color: transparent; max-width: 650px;\" alt=\"\" /></p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px; text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://06.8660.org/file/upload/201604/16/1613132826.jpg\" style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 0px; color: transparent; max-width: 650px;\" alt=\"\" /></p>');
INSERT INTO `sx_article_data_21` VALUES ('83', '&nbsp;<span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px;\">Toblerone这个名字早在1908年就被全世界所知道，一年后，这个独一无二含有杏仁、太妃糖和蜂蜜的巧克力申请了第一个专利：尖顶的三角形包装。</span>\r\n<p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px; text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://img.mp.itc.cn/upload/20160415/74eb3612799f460ca1dc207a770c1d02_th.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 0px; color: transparent; max-width: 600px;\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">今天，瑞士三角巧克力在全世界110多个国家均可见到它可爱的模样！</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px; text-align: center;\"><strong style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">7D芒果干&amp;菲律宾</strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px; text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://img.mp.itc.cn/upload/20160415/c6725d1a878c473a9fefae51f1a653ea_th.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 0px; color: transparent; max-width: 600px;\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">断货王菲律宾7D芒果干，采用芒果肉质最可口的中间部分加工生产而成，跟普通的芒果干根本就不能相提并论！</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px; text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://img.mp.itc.cn/upload/20160415/56f8d516c83e41bf80e42a956df7121c_th.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 0px; color: transparent; max-width: 600px;\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">7D芒果干的果肉肥厚细嫩，色泽很好地保留了芒果诱人的橙黄色。开袋后会闻到自然的芒果香，果肉上面会有芒果脱水后的糖渍渗出来。保留了芒果果肉中含有的大部分维生素C，因此味道不是一味的甜而是甜中带酸，吃起来很有嚼劲。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px; text-align: center;\"><strong style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">综合果蔬干&amp;越南</strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px; text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://img.mp.itc.cn/upload/20160415/5842140bea9f46019d786ae8060870e7_th.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 0px; color: transparent; max-width: 600px;\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">北鼻们的最爱，精挑越南当地优质蔬果果实而成的蔬果干，在加工鲜果成为干制产品的过程中不添加任何化工原料，并以特殊加工方法完全保留果实的品质。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px; text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://img.mp.itc.cn/upload/20160415/4c6ff0360d2043f5860a627c60f23a9c_th.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 0px; color: transparent; max-width: 600px;\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">果蔬干中常见的有菠萝蜜、芋头、红薯、辣椒、秋葵、豆角等等。<span style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">每</span>吃一块都感觉在吃果肉一样。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px; text-align: center;\"><strong style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">麦提莎&amp;英国</strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px; text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://img.mp.itc.cn/upload/20160415/d25c3b3c568849d0990e12f06cdd944b_th.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 0px; color: transparent; max-width: 600px;\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">Maltesers麦提莎外层为巧克力外衣，内含牛奶麦乳精，经典的巧克力球。国内的麦丽素就是模仿的麦提莎。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px; text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://img.mp.itc.cn/upload/20160415/15155ca37e104f60b8534e12bb775a02_th.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 0px; color: transparent; max-width: 600px;\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">但是Maltesers麦提莎吃起来比麦丽素好吃，因为从巧克力及内部奶粉用料来讲，外层香滑巧克力是纯可可脂的，内陷香脆，感觉很纯正。巧克力不会有粉粉的感觉，比较香滑。香浓的巧克力伴着美味的麦心，香甜而不腻！</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px; text-align: center;\"><strong style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">星空糖&amp;美国</strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px; text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://img.mp.itc.cn/upload/20160415/95139e7d10604ce888842c5d74e87c6b_th.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 0px; color: transparent; max-width: 600px;\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">最好吃最好看的棒棒糖，美到不行！据说见证过9万对情侣的甜蜜爱情故事，人称&ldquo;泡妞神器&rdquo;！</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px; text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://img.mp.itc.cn/upload/20160415/7b8ea4e69f2b43b688cf3fc3e4db56f0_th.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 0px; color: transparent; max-width: 600px;\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">纯手工制作，天然健康无添加，高分辨率图像技术，八大行星，和爱人手牵手感受浪漫星空！</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px; text-align: center;\"><strong style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">Knoppers 饼干&amp;德国</strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px; text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://img.mp.itc.cn/upload/20160415/a6214dd0050d400c8715f90e045e5956_th.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 0px; color: transparent; max-width: 600px;\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">威化饼干+奶油+巧克力酱+坚果碎片+薄薄的芝士，口味偏甜。威化饼干带来的蓬松中有芝士的香气，巧克力酱的厚重。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px; text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://img.mp.itc.cn/upload/20160415/da10d91d2ebd4cc18491dfe568e35478_th.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 0px; color: transparent; max-width: 600px;\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">奶油的调和，坚果碎片的口感。香脆的华夫饼 加上浓郁的巧克力酱，创造出无法停止的美味~ 牙齿不好者也可食用，非常松软也不甜。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px; text-align: center;\"><strong style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">樱花曲奇饼干&amp;日本</strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px; text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://img.mp.itc.cn/upload/20160415/793c4eb2af06467b88af8897ea253e82_th.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 0px; color: transparent; max-width: 600px;\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">颜控最爱的一款饼干！绿色的饼干，搭配紫红的整朵盐渍樱花，感觉特别清新。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px;\">　　<img src=\"http://img.mp.itc.cn/upload/20160415/4bf22d72046d4d6281d74af20fabd476_th.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 0px; color: transparent; max-width: 600px;\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">一口咬下去，口感1级棒，饼干的酥脆，抹茶的清香，盐渍樱花的奇特口感，总是让人忍不住再来一片。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><strong style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">马卡龙&amp;法国</strong></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px; text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://img.mp.itc.cn/upload/20160415/30592d94857c41bfacf7c0d096ce5118_th.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 0px; color: transparent; max-width: 600px;\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">巴黎香</span><span style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">榭</span><span style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">丽舍大街排队最长的店毫不夸张，来自世界各地的吃货都慕名而来！</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px; text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://img.mp.itc.cn/upload/20160415/f26df2dd23854afc8c646e84f6c5cd7e_th.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 0px; color: transparent; max-width: 600px;\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">100%来自欧洲的原材料，采用新鲜压制果溶、美帝进口鲜奶油，外酥内柔，让你享受味觉的盛宴！</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><strong style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">蜂蜜黄油薯片&amp;</span><span style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">韩国</span></span></strong></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px; text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://img.mp.itc.cn/upload/20160415/b44f51145b984164a9220c78e37e11c0_th.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 0px; color: transparent; max-width: 600px;\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">韩国号称最土豪薯片，全韩疯抢。这股热潮甚至蔓延至全世界~蜂蜜和黄油的绝妙调味，薯片薄到你尖叫，好吃到无敌！</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px; text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://img.mp.itc.cn/upload/20160415/05306866f44b40b9b52a3472976ec25c_th.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 0px; color: transparent; max-width: 600px;\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">生薯片加上洋槐蜂蜜的甜甜味道，吃起来香酥酥，推出后大受欢迎一直卖断货。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><strong style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">大哥花生豆&amp;泰国</strong></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px; text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://img.mp.itc.cn/upload/20160415/9c2c3dbc3663474cb22047373b28258b_th.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 0px; color: transparent; max-width: 600px;\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text-indent: 0px; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">经典的泰式零食，有鸡味、虾味、椰浆味、烧烤味、芥末味、咖啡味等多种口味，能满足不同人的喜好。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 26px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 26px; text