INSERT INTO `sx_brand_data_13` VALUES ('4', '&nbsp;<span style=\"color: rgb(40, 40, 40); font-family: \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\'; line-height: 24px;\">两个人吃4人份的团购，差不多都吃完了。服务很好，主动下菜加水很积极，特定的食材大致需要烫多久都会主动说明。锅底就是清鸡汤，不加盐不加味精，喝上去只有淡淡的鸡汤味，吃惯了重口味的四川火锅试试这种感觉会更健康。牛肉非常棒，很嫩很嫩，涮15秒就能吃，配上他们的调料感觉很适合，不会太抢菜的味道。龙趸鱼也很新鲜，吃上去口感很好。这两个菜是最满意的。反而那个北海道螃蟹真的很一般，端上来就是熟的，吃上去有点像大闸蟹又没有大闸蟹好吃，最后放锅里涮下勉强吃掉了。猪肉取的是猪身上各个部位的肉，感觉还是挺好玩的，可以吃出来不同位置的区别，不过还是牛肉更好吃哈～别的菜基本上无功无过吧，刺身还算新鲜，在锅烧开前可以垫垫肚子，但是芥末不是现磨的，是那种管状的，太冲，不太喜欢。总体来说按照团购的价格还是很不错的，食材确实很好。\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://06.8660.org/file/upload/201603/23/1621198135.jpg\" alt=\"cX_Dg6Icr6I_b5NLd6GsD0gk82fgks3vF46ic3VUwC5CUbge5HlxwvWKA3naZwMDTYGVDmosZWTLal1WbWRW3A\" width=\"525\" height=\"700\" /><img src=\"http://06.8660.org/file/upload/201603/23/1621339035.jpg\" alt=\"PcGWwIAtrtLqZtlqxA5yZR_XxdgTrWjjKNAAJ0ooB1oM_mJet2qLpG8XZRY-E7rlTYGVDmosZWTLal1WbWRW3A\" width=\"525\" height=\"700\" /></div>\r\n</span>');
INSERT INTO `sx_brand_data_13` VALUES ('5', '&nbsp;<span style=\"color: rgb(40, 40, 40); font-family: \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\'; line-height: 24px;\">环境非常不错，大堂是古风的装修风格，感觉座位之间间隔小了一点。不过用餐体验应该可以。包间的话配备很齐全，大玻璃落地窗很美。</span><br style=\"color: rgb(40, 40, 40); font-family: \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\'; line-height: 24px;\" />\r\n<br style=\"color: rgb(40, 40, 40); font-family: \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\'; line-height: 24px;\" />\r\n<span style=\"color: rgb(40, 40, 40); font-family: \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\'; line-height: 24px;\">重点说一下菜式吧，说实在的有一点失望，很多招牌菜没有想象中好吃。</span><br style=\"color: rgb(40, 40, 40); font-family: \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\'; line-height: 24px;\" />\r\n<br style=\"color: rgb(40, 40, 40); font-family: \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\'; line-height: 24px;\" />\r\n<span style=\"color: rgb(40, 40, 40); font-family: \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\'; line-height: 24px;\">招牌黑叉烧拼盘：真的如传说中一样太肥太肥了，一咬一口油一口渣，个人不太喜欢，不是特别喜欢吃油腻的还是不要点了&hellip;&hellip;</span><br style=\"color: rgb(40, 40, 40); font-family: \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\'; line-height: 24px;\" />\r\n<br style=\"color: rgb(40, 40, 40); font-family: \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\'; line-height: 24px;\" />\r\n<span style=\"color: rgb(40, 40, 40); font-family: \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\'; line-height: 24px;\">盆菜：这个价格应该不菲，不过的确挺好吃的，有很大的瑶柱和杏鲍菇，鹅掌也不错，发菜也有。过年图个好意头。</span><br style=\"color: rgb(40, 40, 40); font-family: \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\'; line-height: 24px;\" />\r\n<br style=\"color: rgb(40, 40, 40); font-family: \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\'; line-height: 24px;\" />\r\n<span style=\"color: rgb(40, 40, 40); font-family: \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\'; line-height: 24px;\">避风塘炒蟹：不知道是不是这个名字，不过这个跟价格不对等啦&hellip;没有肉的&hellip;都是空壳子，点了没人吃。</span><br style=\"color: rgb(40, 40, 40); font-family: \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\'; line-height: 24px;\" />\r\n<br style=\"color: rgb(40, 40, 40); font-family: \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\'; line-height: 24px;\" />\r\n<span style=\"color: rgb(40, 40, 40); font-family: \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\'; line-height: 24px;\">白切鸡：还不错，正常水准吧，肉不老，不过也不是特别惊艳。</span><br style=\"color: rgb(40, 40, 40); font-family: \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\'; line-height: 24px;\" />\r\n<br style=\"color: rgb(40, 40, 40); font-family: \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\'; line-height: 24px;\" />\r\n<span style=\"color: rgb(40, 40, 40); font-family: \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\'; line-height: 24px;\">鱼头：有点辣，还算好吃，不腥。</span><br style=\"color: rgb(40, 40, 40); font-family: \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\'; line-height: 24px;\" />\r\n<br style=\"color: rgb(40, 40, 40); font-family: \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\'; line-height: 24px;\" />\r\n<span style=\"color: rgb(40, 40, 40); font-family: \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\'; line-height: 24px;\">大虾：个头的确感人，肉质也很扎实，推荐，很好看。</span><br style=\"color: rgb(40, 40, 40); font-family: \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\'; line-height: 24px;\" />\r\n<br style=\"color: rgb(40, 40, 40); font-family: \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\'; line-height: 24px;\" />\r\n<span style=\"color: rgb(40, 40, 40); font-family: \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\'; line-height: 24px;\">大菠萝包：据说还得提前预定，的确很讨喜的样子，不过太大了有点腻，基本没有馅，酥皮好吃。</span><br style=\"color: rgb(40, 40, 40); font-family: \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\'; line-height: 24px;\" />\r\n<br style=\"color: rgb(40, 40, 40); font-family: \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\'; line-height: 24px;\" />\r\n<span style=\"color: rgb(40, 40, 40); font-family: \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\'; line-height: 24px;\">炸馄饨：还可以，分量有点大，沾料不错。</span><br style=\"color: rgb(40, 40, 40); font-family: \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\'; line-height: 24px;\" />\r\n<br style=\"color: rgb(40, 40, 40); font-family: \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\'; line-height: 24px;\" />\r\n<span style=\"color: rgb(40, 40, 40); font-family: \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\'; line-height: 24px;\">虎皮尖椒：还不错卖相好看也好吃。</span><br style=\"color: rgb(40, 40, 40); font-family: \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\'; line-height: 24px;\" />\r\n<br style=\"color: rgb(40, 40, 40); font-family: \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\'; line-height: 24px;\" />\r\n<span style=\"color: rgb(40, 40, 40); font-family: \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\'; line-height: 24px;\">三种年糕：煎的，还挺好吃的。</span><br style=\"color: rgb(40, 40, 40); font-family: \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\'; line-height: 24px;\" />\r\n<br style=\"color: rgb(40, 40, 40); font-family: \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\'; line-height: 24px;\" />\r\n<span style=\"color: rgb(40, 40, 40); font-family: \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\'; line-height: 24px;\">山水豆腐：的确还可以，很多人推荐。</span><br style=\"color: rgb(40, 40, 40); font-family: \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\'; line-height: 24px;\" />\r\n<br style=\"color: rgb(40, 40, 40); font-family: \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\'; line-height: 24px;\" />\r\n<span style=\"color: rgb(40, 40, 40); font-family: \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\'; line-height: 24px;\">总体还可以吧，点了好多菜都没怎么吃，最后剩了好多&hellip;没有特别惊喜的感觉吧。应该&hellip;&hellip;人少的话绝对不会去，太贵不划算。\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://06.8660.org/file/upload/201603/23/1641485926.jpg\" alt=\"pNLoVqrmRQaSXYHUXhQy1klLJ2im0WyrJLsApi18YclGLvYeIYNvHTjayCt6Fap-CjM_FsO3sW809PHY7spB8g\" width=\"249\" height=\"177\" /></div>\r\n</span>');
